ough-energy-to-invest-rs-450-cr-to-set-up-20gwh-equipment-factory-124031900487_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%20Dismissing%20Doubts%20Over%20EVMs%2C%20EC%20Must%20Know%20It%20Can't%20Promise%20a%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20March%2016%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20snubbed%20the%20Doubting%20Thomases%20who%20question%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20(which%20most%20of%20the%20electorate%20do).%20He%20was%20at%20his%20poetic%20best%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20EVM%20doubters%20by%20sharing%20an%20Urdu%20couplet%20he%20had%20penned%20on%20how%20the%20machines%20would%20have%20themselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsundayguardianlive.com%2Fnews%2Fcec-snubs-those-doubting-evms%5C%22%3Eresponded%20to%20such%20allegations.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAdhooree%20hasaraton%20ka%20iljaam%20har%20baar%20ham%20par%20lagana%20theek%20nahin%2C%20vafa%20khud%20se%20nahin%20hoti%2C%20khata%20EVM%20ki%20kahate%20ho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20blame%20us%20every%20time%20for%20unfulfilled%20desires.%20While%20you%20fail%20to%20prove%20yourself%2C%20you%20say%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20EVM).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECEC%20mocked%20democratic%20voices%20when%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fvideos%2Ftoi-original%2Fchief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-mocks-social-media-evm-experts-amid-laughs%2Fvideoshow%2F108548564.cms%5C%22%3Ederided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20political%20parties%2C%20social%20media%20and%20EVM%20experts%20demanding%20the%20banning%20of%20EVMs%20amid%20laughs%20saying%20that%20the%20machines%20made%20the%20poll%20process%20fairer%20and%20better%20and%20expressed%20his%20expert%20opinion%20that%20all%20parties%20know%20this%20in%20their%20hearts.%20And%20he%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20courts%20have%20certified%20the%20integrity%20of%20these%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-indias-elections-free-and-fair%5C%22%3EAre%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%20Free%20and%20Fair%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20utterances%20expose%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20ignorance%20of%20the%20basic%20concept%20of%20elections%20and%20democracy.%20His%20comment%20that%20only%20those%20who%20lose%20elections%20question%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20implies%20that%20elections%20are%20only%20meant%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20candidates%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fallacy.%20He%20should%20know%20that%20in%20a%20democracy%20sovereignty%20vests%20with%20the%20citizens%20and%20elections%20are%20the%20tool%20for%20the%20citizens%20to%20transfer%20this%20sovereignty%20to%20his%2Fher%20chosen%20representative%20once%20in%20five%20years.%20To%20do%20so%20elections%20and%20voting%20system%20must%20adhere%20to%20certain%20%E2%80%9Cdemocratic%20principles%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20voting%20process%20should%20be%20transparent%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20the%20general%20public%20can%20be%20satisfied%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20correctly%20recorded%20and%20counted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20voting%20and%20counting%20process%20should%20be%20publicly%20auditable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20should%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20essential%20steps%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20should%20be%20verifiability%20in%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20and%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results%20reliably%20without%20too%20much%20special%20knowledge.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20election%20process%20should%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20and%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20should%20be%20in%20full%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20voting%20process%2C%20and%20the%20public%20at%20large%20should%20be%20able%20to%20verify%20the%20casting%20and%20counting%20of%20their%20votes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EElectronic%20processes%20and%20technological%20practices%20should%20be%20subject%20to%20public%20scrutiny%2Fexaminability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20voting%2Fcounting%20system%20must%20ensure%20that%20the%20voter%20should%20have%20the%20knowledge%20that%20her%20vote%20is%20cast%20as%20intended%2C%20recorded%20as%20cast%20and%20counted%20as%20recorded.%20Why%20has%20not%20the%20CEC%20ever%20responded%20to%20this%20critical%20poser%20raised%20by%20several%20sources%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconstitutionalconduct.files.wordpress.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fcitizens-commission-on-elections-vol.-i.pdf%5C%22%3EReport%20of%20the%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20(CCE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20headed%20by%20a%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20which%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20ECI%20in%20January%2FFebruary%202021%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20to%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20half-baked%20poetry%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20right%20to%20blame%20us%20every%20time%20for%20unfulfilled%20desires.%20While%20you%20fail%20to%20prove%20yourself%2C%20you%20say%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20EVM.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20CEC%20go%20through%20the%20report%20of%20the%20CCE%2C%20the%20expert%20group%20which%20had%20reviewed%20the%20functioning%20of%20EVMs%20primarily%20on%20the%20touchstone%20of%20whether%20and%20how%20far%20their%20use%20complied%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98democracy%20principles.%E2%80%99%20In%20short%2C%20it%20insists%20on%20absolute%20transparency%20in%20facilitating%20the%20voter%20to%20exercise%20his%20or%20her%20choice%20and%20in%20ensuring%20that%20these%20selections%20are%2C%20indeed%2C%20reflected%20in%20the%20stored%20vote%20and%20counted%20as%20such%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20slightest%20deviation%20whatsoever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08202025%2FUntitled-design-36-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Voters%20at%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20Bangalore%20during%202009%20general%20elections.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FRanjit%20Bhaskar%2FCC%20BY-SA%202.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20principles%20also%20mandate%20that%20the%20voting%20procedure%20is%20easily%20understandable%20and%20verifiable%20by%20the%20voter%20and%20open%20to%20audit%20without%20complications%20even%20when%20relevant%20technology%20is%20utilised.%20There%20should%20be%20absolutely%20no%20scope%20for%20error%20or%20misrepresentation%20of%20the%20elector%E2%80%99s%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCE%20had%20relied%20on%20depositions%20and%20opinions%20of%20several%20national%20and%20international%20experts%20and%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20countries%20do%20not%20prefer%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%20during%20polls.%20Among%20the%20domain%20knowledge%20holders%20who%20submitted%20deposition%20before%20this%20CCE%20group%20were%20Ronald%20L.%20Rivest%20of%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Cambridge%2C%20USA%3B%20Alex%20Halderman%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20USA%3B%20Poorvi%20L.%20Vora%20and%20Bhagirath%20Narahari%20of%20George%20Washington%20University%2C%20USA%3B%20Alok%20Choudhary%20of%20North-western%20University%2C%20USA%20Sandeep%20Shukla%2C%20Professor%2C%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%2C%20IIT%20Kanpur%3B%20Douglas%20W.%20Jones%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Iowa%2C%20USA%3B%20Nasir%20Memon%20of%20New%20York%20University%20(Brooklyn)%2C%20USA%3B%20Philip%20B.%20Stark%20of%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20Vanessa%20Teague%2C%20Associate%20Professor%2C%20School%20of%20Computing%20and%20Information%20Systems%2C%20University%20of%20Melbourne%2C%20Cybersecurity%2C%20Australia%3B%20Bappa%20Sinha%20of%20Free%20Software%20Movement%20of%20India%2C%20Subodh%20Sharma%20of%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20and%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Public%20Policy%2C%20IIT%2C%20Delhi%3B%20KV%20Subrahmanyam%2C%20Professor%2C%20Computer%20Science%2C%20Chennai%20Mathematical%20Institute%2C%20Chennai%3B%20Dr%20Sanjiva%20Prasad%20and%20Dr.%20Subhashis%20Banerjee%20of%20IIT%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Anupam%20Saraf%2C%20Professor%20and%20Future%20Designer%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20best%20brains%20on%20the%20subject%20across%20the%20globe%20and%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20put%20together%20another%20group%20to%20match%20this%20vast%20and%20varied%20expertise.%20And%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20CCE%20report%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDue%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20End-to-End%20(E2E)%20verifiability%2C%20the%20present%20EVM%2FVVAPAT%20system%20is%20not%20verifiable%20and%20therefore%20is%20unfit%20for%20democratic%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat%20an%20EVM%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20detected%20to%20have%20been%20hacked%20provides%20no%20guarantee%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20hacked.%20Thus%2C%20elections%20must%20be%20conducted%20assuming%20that%20the%20EVMs%20may%20possibly%20be%20tampered%20with.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20practice%2C%20it%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20test%20more%20EVMs%20than%20even%20what%20the%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20demand%20(30%25%20and%2050%25%20respectively)%20to%20ensure%20verification%20and%20reliable%20ascertainment%20of%20results.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20must%20be%20stringent%20pre-audit%20of%20the%20electronic%20vote%20count%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20The%20audit%20may%20in%20some%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20depending%20on%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20%E2%80%93%20require%20a%20full%20manual%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20electronic%20voting%20system%20should%20be%20re-designed%20to%20be%20software%20and%20hardware%20independent%20in%20order%20to%20be%20verifiable%20or%20auditable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20should%20know%20that%20none%20in%20the%20CCE%20or%20those%20who%20deposed%20had%20%E2%80%9Cunfulfilled%20desires%E2%80%9D%20to%20capture%20political%20power%20by%20any%20means%20and%20did%20not%20fault%20the%20EVM%20for%20failing%20to%20do%20so!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%5C%22%3EThe%20Case%20for%20Bringing%20Paper%20Ballots%20Back%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntegrity%20of%20EVMs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20to%20the%20falsehood%20about%20the%20courts%20certifying%20the%20integrity%20of%20EVMs.%20The%20first%20serious%20legal%20challenge%20to%20EVMs%20was%20made%20by%20Dr%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20of%20BJP%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20vourt%20in%20W.P.(C)%20No.%2011879%20of%202009%20and%20this%20was%20the%20verdict%20in%20January%202012%3A%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDr.%20Swamy%20is%20right%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20that%20EVMs%20may%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20frauds.%C2%A0%20There%20may%20be%20security%20issues%20as%20well%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swamy%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%20On%20October%208%2C%202013%20the%20Court%20confirming%20the%20doubts%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20EVMs%20mandated%20the%20use%20of%20voter%20verified%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20system%20in%20a%20phased%20manner%20to%20bring%20about%20some%20semblance%20of%20democratic%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20materials%20placed%20by%20both%20the%20sides%2C%20we%20are%20satisfied%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98paper%20trail%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20indispensable%20requirement%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20The%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20EVMs%20can%20be%20achieved%20only%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98paper%20trail%E2%80%99.%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20ensure%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20voting%20system.%20With%20an%20intent%20to%20have%20fullest%20transparency%20in%20the%20system%20and%20to%20restore%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20set%20up%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20system%20because%20vote%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20act%20of%20expression%20which%20has%20immense%20importance%20in%20democratic%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20introduced%20thus%20has%20been%20morphed%20into%20a%20meaningless%20bioscope%20is%20another%20story!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writer%20himself%20had%20filed%20W.P(C)%201514%20of%202018%20titled%20%3Cem%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20%26amp%3B%20Ors.%20v.%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20which%20vide%20judgement%20reported%20as%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20(2019)%2015%20SCC%20377%2C%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20ECI%20had%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpointed%20out%20infrastructure%20difficulties%2C%20including%20manpower%20availability%2C%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%20in%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20EVMs%20for%20verification%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20which%20the%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdeclaration%20of%20result%20of%20election%20could%20be%20delayed%20by%205-6%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20directed%20the%20ECI%20to%20count%20VVPATs%20in%20five%20polling%20stations%20per%20assembly%20constituency%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20prayer%20in%20the%20writ%20petition%20for%20counting%20of%2030%25%20VVPATs%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%20had%20found%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20proximity%20to%20the%20election%20schedule%20announced%20by%20the%20ECI%20must%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20significantly%2C%20vide%20the%20same%20order%2C%20Writ%20Petition%20(C)%20No.%2023%20of%202019%20was%20disposed%20of%20by%20the%20Court%20expressing%20its%20%E2%80%9Creluctance%20to%20go%20into%20the%20issues%20regarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20EVMs%20which%20have%20been%20raised%20at%20a%20belated%20stage.%20The%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20month%20of%20December%202018%20raising%20various%20technical%20issues%20which%20are%20not%20possible%20to%20be%20gone%20into%20at%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20a%20CEC%20utter%20such%20falsehood%3F%20As%20an%20ordinary%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20the%20CEC%20one%20question.%20As%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20totally%20partisan%20way%20in%20which%20CEC%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20are%20being%20selected%20and%20appointed%20and%20the%20alienation%20of%20the%20Commission%20from%20the%20public%20and%20political%20opposition%2C%20the%20credibility%20of%20ECI%20is%20at%20a%20very%20low%20ebb.%20Why%20is%20he%20lowering%20it%20further%20by%20serenading%20the%20Black-Box%20called%20EVM%20which%20can%20be%20grossly%20misused%20for%20bulk-manufacturing%20of%20votes%20to%20steal%20peoples%E2%80%99%20mandate%3F%C2%A0%20And%20in%20the%20process%20mocking%20the%20people%20who%20seek%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%3F%20Pray%2C%20is%20this%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20ECI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710844154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fby-dismissing-doubts-over-evms-ec-must-know-it-cant-promise-a-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20snub%20against%20EVM%20doubters%20by%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20that%20it%20is%20'wrong%20to%20blame%20EVMs%20for%20your%20unfulfilled%20desires'%20expose%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20ignorance%20of%20the%20basic%20concept%20of%20elections%20and%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fby-dismissing-doubts-over-evms-ec-must-know-it-cant-promise-a-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Adolf%20Hitler%20Was%20Arrested%20By%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20In%20Meghalaya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdolf%20Lu%20Hitler%20arrested%20by%20John%20F%20Kennedy%26quot%3B%2C%20read%20newspaper%20headlines%20during%20the%202008%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20piquing%20interest%20of%20people%20across%20the%20country%20given%20the%20historical%20significance%20of%20the%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20so%20happened%20that%20then%20NCP%20candidate%20Adolf%20Hitler%20was%20arrested%20by%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20during%20campaigning%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20newspapers%20splashed%20the%20headline%20%26quot%3BAdolf%20Lu%20Hitler%20Arrested%20by%20John%20F%20Kennedy%26quot%3B.%20The%20headlines%20quickly%20became%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town%2C%20and%20would%20have%20been%20viral%2C%20if%20social%20media%20was%20as%20prominent%20as%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdolf%20Hitler%20later%20won%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20