%20precedes%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IPL%20will%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20There%20is%20no%20other%20cricket%20happening.%20The%20eyes%20of%20the%20world%20are%20on%20IPL.%20This%20is%20where%20you%20can%20snatch%20a%20berth%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20not%20only%20Indians%2C%20even%20the%20foreign%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview%20facilitated%20by%20the%20IPL's%20official%20TV%20broadcaster%20'Star%20Sports'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20have%20not%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20T20%20cricket%20since%20the%202022%20edition%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20on%20the%20flight%20to%20USA%20and%20Caribbean%20for%20the%20ICC%20showpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20the%20veteran%20batters%20still%20add%20value%20to%20the%20T20%20squad%3F%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20be%20needed%20there.%20These%20are%20giants%20of%20cricketing%20world.%20Form%20is%20like%20the%20morning%20dew%2C%20it%20can%20elude%20you%20but%20class%20of%20these%20people%20has%20stamp%20of%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20rate%20Kohli%20as%20the%20greatest%20Indian%20batsman%20for%20the%20simple%20reason%2C%20his%20fitness%2C%20he%20is%20getting%20fitter%20with%20age%20like%20old%20wine%20does.%20Technically%20very%20sound%20and%20he%20has%20the%20uncanny%20knack%20of%20adapting%20to%20all%20three%20formats%2C%20same%20goes%20for%20Rohit%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20explained%20in%20his%20inimitable%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20quality%20players.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20about%20Rohit's%20fitness%20levels.%20With%20age%20you%20tend%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20your%20reflexes%20tend%20to%20go.%20Sehwag%20with%20those%20glasses%2C%20his%20reflexes%20were%20not%20the%20same%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20in%20the%20IPL.%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20closely%20tracked%20India's%20campaign%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20where%20the%20hosts%20ended%20as%20runners-up%20after%20being%20the%20sole%20unbeaten%20side%20in%20the%20group%20stages.%20The%20final%20loss%20extended%20their%20long%20wait%20for%20a%20world%20title%20but%20Sidhu%20isn't%20too%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20recent%20World%20Cup%20they%20were%20playing%20very%20well%2C%20they%20just%20had%20one%20bad%20game%2C%20one%20bad%20game%20cannot%20asses%20the%20fortunes%20of%20a%20team.%20I%20see%20the%20Indian%20team%20ruling%20the%20roost%20for%20a%20long%20time%20because%20the%20system%20that%20breeds%20cricketers%20is%20very%20congenial%20and%20conducive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20time%2C%20people%20would%20carry%20on%20despite%20bad%20form%20because%20there%20were%20no%20replacements.%20Now%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20replacing%20the%20Indian%20captain%20as%20captain%20at%20Mumbai%20Indians%20because%20he%20has%20performed%20so%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20that%20it%20is%20derogatory%20to%20Rohit%20but%20it%20is%20just%20a%20thought%20process.%20The%20old%20order%20must%20change%20yielding%20place%20to%20the%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sidhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20multiple%20options%20for%20wicket-keeper%20batter's%20slot%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20squad%20with%20likes%20of%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%2C%20and%20K%20L%20Rahul%20in%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESidhu%20said%20he%20would%20go%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20superior%20keeping%20skills%20with%20his%20batting%20prowess%20being%20%26quot%3Bsecondary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20take%20to%20commentary%20like%20fish%20to%20water%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20while%20since%20the%2060-year-old%20held%20the%20mic%20but%20three%20days%20from%20his%20%26quot%3Bfirst%26quot%3B%20commentary%20comeback%2C%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20was%20as%20gung-ho%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoss%2C%20cricket%20is%20my%20first%20love.%20If%20your%20hobby%20becomes%20your%20profession%20there%20is%20nothing%20better%20than%20that.%20A%20duckling%20would%20never%20forget%20how%20to%20swim%2C%20I%20will%20take%20to%20commentary%20like%20a%20fish%20takes%20to%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20sense%20of%20humour%20kept%20him%20going%20during%20the%20turbulent%20phases%20of%20his%20life%2C%20Sidhu%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSecret%20of%20my%20life%20is%20that%20is%20I%20switch%20on%20and%20switch%20off.%20It%20was%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20switch%20off%20from%20politics%20but%20then%20the%20age%20of%20miracles%20has%20not%20passed.%20The%20difficult%20is%20done%20at%20once%2C%20the%20impossible%20takes%20a%20little%20while%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mental%20fortitude%20will%20sail%20me%20through%20any%20situation%20now.%20In%20cricket%2C%20I%20have%20made%2020%20odd%20comebacks%2C%20this%20is%20my%20first%20comeback%20to%20commentary.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20swing%20of%20things%20from%201999%20to%202014-15%20(commentary).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20gem%20cannot%20be%20polished%20without%20friction%20nor%20a%20man%20perfected%20without%20trials%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20went%20on%2C%20the%20way%20only%20he%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20Sidhu%20provided%20the%20X%20factor%20to%20the%20commentary%20box%20and%20the%20stupendous%20success%20behind%20the%20mic%20made%20him%20a%20prominent%20face%20in%20the%20entertainment%20world%20where%20he%20was%20paid%20handsomely%20to%20appear%20on%20a%20comedy%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20what%20he%20could%20make%20as%20an%20established%20India%20cricketer%20but%20Sidhu%20said%20he%20was%20never%20in%20it%20for%20the%20big%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20left%20cricket%20and%20joined%20commentary%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20this%20is%20something%20I%20could%20do.%20I%20was%20not%20very%20confident%20(initially)%20but%2010-15%20days%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20word%20Sidhuism%20came%20up.%20I%20was%20walking%20in%20a%20lane%20no%20one%20was%20walking.%20It%20was%20the%20lane%20of%20Sidhuism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Rs%2060-70%20lakh%20for%20the%20whole%20tournament%2C%20I%20was%20taking%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20per%20day%20in%20IPL.%20The%20satisfaction%20was%20not%20with%20money%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20was%20that%20time%20would%20fly.%20It%20was%20beautiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710843720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2gpmf01g_sidhu_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwas-taking-rs-25-lakh-per-day-in-ipl-navjot-singh-sidhu-confirms-commentary-return-5267725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20money%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20what%20he%20could%20make%20as%20an%20established%20India%20cricketer%20but%20Sidhu%20said%20he%20was%20never%20in%20it%20for%20the%20big%20bucks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Aaradhya%20confidently%20posed%20for%20the%20shutterbugs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710843193000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108616038%2Cimgsize-29548.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-aaradhya-bachchan-confidently-posed-for-the-shutterbugs-at-the-airport%2Farticleshow%2F108616038.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108616038.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20Aaradhy