ssinsider.com%2Fmom-gave-her-8-year-old-a-cellphone-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20cellphone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He'd%20been%20asking%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20was%20now%20less%20adamant%20that%20we%20wait%20as%20long%20as%20possible%20to%20give%20in.%20I%20knew%20that%20despite%20my%20resistance%2C%20the%20day%20he'd%20receive%20a%20phone%20number%20of%20his%20own%20was%20coming%20quickly.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20start%20of%206th%20grade%2C%20we'll%20get%20you%20a%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20agreed.%20I%20had%20the%20summer%20to%20adjust%20my%20mindset%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20little%20kid%20anymore%20and%20soon%20he'd%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20world%20virtually.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBuying%20my%20son%20a%20phone%20wasn't%20my%20first%20choice.%20I%20often%20wish%20I%20could%20raise%20my%20children%20in%20the%2090s%20to%20avoid%20the%20dangers%20that%20come%20along%20with%20today's%20technology.%20I%20didn't%20want%20him%20texting%20incessantly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-popular-kids-videos-with-billions-in-views-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewatching%20YouTube%20videos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20his%20bus%20ride%20to%20school%2C%20or%20having%20a%20device%20to%20distract%20him%20from%20the%20people%20around%20him.%20I%20also%20worried%20he'd%20naively%20connect%20with%20strangers.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20few%20kids%20his%20age%20without%20a%20cellphone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanley-cups-tearing-apart-gen-alpha-middle-schools-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emiddle%20school%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20activities%20widening%2C%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20call%20me%2