p%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizenship%20Amendment%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20CAA.%20The%20court%20also%20gave%20the%20government%20three%20weeks%20-%20till%20April%208%20-%20to%20respond%20to%20237%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20law%20that%20was%20notified%20last%20week%2C%20days%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flok-sabha-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20petitioners%20were%20given%20leave%20to%20approach%20if%20citizenship%20is%20granted%20to%20any%20individual%20before%20that%20date%3B%20senior%20lawyers%20Kapil%20Sibal%20and%20Indira%20Jaising%20both%20made%20that%20request%2C%20as%20Solicitor-General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20(appearing%20for%20the%20government)%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20making%20any%20statement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20had%20originally%20sought%20four%20weeks'%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20affidavit%2C%20on%20merits%2C%20to%20237%20petitions.%2020%20interim%20applications%20are%20already%20filed%20and%20many%20are%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20Realistically%2C%20we%20need%20four%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20heard%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra.%20The%20petitioners%20included%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20(a%20Kerala-based%20political%20party)%20and%20also%20opposition%20leaders%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20Mahua%20Moitra%20of%20the%20Trinamool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-supreme-court-before-chief-justice-led-bench-today-challenges-to-citizenship-law-caa-5266335%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizenship%20Act%20Unconstitutional%3F%20237%20Petitions%20Before%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%20has%20been%20set%20for%20April%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20-%20who%20did%20not%20oppose%20the%20request%20for%20more%20time%20-%20have%20sought%20a%20pause%20on%20implementation%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20CAA%2C%20which%20they%20have%20said%20is%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20told%20the%20court%20they%20would%20not%20oppose%20the%20government's%20request%20for%20more%20time%20to%20study%20the%20challenges%2C%20but%20urged%20the%20Chief%20Justice-led%20bench%20to%20order%20a%20stay%20on%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20after%20the%20citizenship%20bill%20was%20cleared%20by%20Parliament%2C%20multiple%20challenges%20were%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20pause%20implementation%20as%20the%20rules%20had%20not%20been%20notified.%20Last%20week%2C%20arguing%20in%20this%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20that%20situation%20did%20not%20apply%20now%2C%20since%20the%20rules%20are%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmisplaced-misinformed-unwarranted-india-on-us-caa-remarks-5243584%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMisplaced%2C%20Misinformed%2C%20Unwarranted%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20US'%20CAA%20Remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is...%20notification%20was%20issued%20after%20four%20years.%20Under%20the%20law%2C%20rules%20have%20to%20be%20notified%20within%20six%20months.%20Now%20the%20problem%20is%20-%20if%20somebody%20gets%20citizenship%2C%20it%20will%20be%20impossible%20to%20reverse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20by%20the%20court%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20government's%20request%20for%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20(in%202019)%20they%20were%20not%20notifying%20rules%2C%20so%20no%20stay%20was%20granted.%20There%20is%20no%20question%20of%20'rejection%20of%20stay'%20(in%20the%20earlier%20instance)...%20then%20there%20were%20no%20rules%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20court%2C%20laying%20out%20his%20argument%20for%20a%20stay%20till%20the%20challenges%20to%20the%20citizenship%20law%20are%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20have%20they%20waited%20for%20four%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20referring%20to%20allegations%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20that%20implementation%20was%20delayed%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20have%20as%20much%20time%2C%20but%20don't%20grant%20citizenship%20in%20meantime%2C%26quot%3B%20Indira%20Jaising%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20then%20said%20the%20fact%20the%20rules%20were%20notified%20before%20an%20election%20was%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-caa-news-governments-explainer-on-citizenship-law-amid-opposition-attacks-5230003%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGovernment%20Clarifies%20Citizenship%20Law%20Amid%20Opposition%20Attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20CAA%2C%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20fleeing%20religious%20persecution%20can%20seek%20citizenship.%20Persons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20these%20three%20nations%20are%20eligible%20if%20they%20entered%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20slammed%20the%20government%20over%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20law's%20implementation%20-%20four%20years%20after%20it%20cleared%20the%20Parliament%20and%20days%20before%20a%20general%20election.%20The%20move%20is%20%26quot%3Bevidently%20designed%20to%20polarise%20the%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Assam%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20boss%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20doubts%20the%20law's%20legality%20and%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20%26quot%3Bsnatch%20citizenship%20rights%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20say%20CAA%20gives%20you%20rights.%20But%20the%20moment%20you%20apply%20for%20citizenship%2C%20you%20become%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20you%20will%20lose%20your%20rights.%20You%20will%20lose%20rights%20and%20be%20taken%20to%20detention%20camps.%20Please%20think%20before%20you%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20trashed%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNot%20Anti-Muslim%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20On%20Opposition%20Attacks%20On%20CAA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20the%20CAA%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20resorting%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20lies%26quot%3B.%20On%20the%20timing%20question%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%20that%20it%20will%20bring%20CAA%20and%20provide%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20refugees%20(from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan).%20BJP%20has%20a%20clear%20agenda%20and%20under%20that%20promise%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20in%202019.%20It%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20Covid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%2