ent%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20the%20development%20and%20prosperity%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20From%20free%20medical%20treatment%20to%20providing%20tap%20water%20connections%20in%20homes%2C%20from%20free%20ration%20facilities%20to%20benefiting%20women%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20through%20MUDRA%20Yojana%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20to%20give%20the%20best%2C%20to%20serve%20the%20best%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20also%20confident%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20would%20repose%20its%20faith%20in%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20decided%20that%20on%20April%2019%2C%20every%20vote%20will%20go%20to%20BJP%20and%20NDA.%20Now%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20decided%20-%20this%20time%20it%20will%20cross%20400%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20also%20felicitated%20during%20his%20public%20meeting%20in%20Salem%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam-led%20Secular%20Progressive%20Alliance%2C%20which%20comprised%20INC%2C%20VCK%2C%20MDMK%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20IUML%2C%20MMK%2C%20KMDK%2C%20TVK%2C%20AIFB%2C%20registered%20a%20landslide%20victory%20by%20winning%2038%20of%20the%2039%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20DMK%20won%2023%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20with%2033.2%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%20Congress%20bagged%208%20seats%20with%2012.9%20per%20cent%20vote%20and%20CPI%20won%202%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20CPI(M)%20got%20a%20seat%2C%20IML%20won%201%20seat%20and%20independents%20were%20elected%20on%202%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMK%2C%20a%20political%20party%20that%20mostly%20represents%20the%20Vanniyar%20minority%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20was%20the%20second%20main%20alliance%20partner%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%202019%2C%20which%20contested%20on%20seven%20alliance%20seats.%20With%20a%20vote%20perc