upreme%20Court%20has%20recently%20struck%20two%20salutary%20blows%20to%20bring%20an%20increasingly%20derailed%20democracy%20back%20on%20track.%20This%20by%20first%20pronouncing%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20system%20of%20political%20funding%20unconstitutional%2C%20and%20a%20potential%20breeding%20ground%20for%20quid%20pro%20quos%2C%20even%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%2C%20second%2C%20by%20cancelling%20an%20indulgent%20immunity%20thus%20far%20enjoyed%20by%20legislators%20in%20denoting%20gratifications%20received%20either%20to%20cast%20votes%20or%20make%20lobbyist%20speeches%20in%20parliament%20and%20assemblies%20as%20legislative%20privilege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20squarely%20calling%20the%20practice%20by%20its%20proper%20name%2C%20ergo%20bribery%2C%20has%20struck%20this%20down%20and%20held%20such%20subjects%20to%20be%20liable%20to%20criminal%20procedures%20just%20as%20any%20common%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20best%20of%20our%20anticipation%2C%20these%20two%20initiatives%20will%20not%20but%20clean%20up%20much%20that%20has%20gone%20wrong%20with%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20biggest%20distortion%2C%20we%20are%20afraid%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20set%20right%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20goes%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20representative%20government%20as%20being%20the%20foundation%20of%20democracy%20before%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nearly%2045%25%20of%20MLAs%20Who%20Defected%20Between%202016%20and%202020%20Joined%20the%20BJP%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmlas-defection-2016-2020-bjp-congress-adr%5C%22%3ENearly%2045%25%20of%20MLAs%20Who%20Defected%20Between%202016%20and%202020%20Joined%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizen%20seeks%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20of%20the%20defecting%20legislator%20of%20a%20given%20ideology%2Fpolitical%20party%3A%C2%A0%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20it%20that%20you%20so%20cavalierly%20abuse%20my%20franchise%20by%20crossing%20over%20to%20an%20outfit%20I%20did%20not%20vote%20you%20to%20without%20my%20say%20so%3F%C2%A0Having%20gone%20over%20to%20a%20rival%20party%2C%20you%20no%20longer%20represent%20me%20and%20the%20constituency%20that%20sent%20you%20to%20the%20legislature.%C2%A0In%20your%20new%20avatar%20thus%20you%20occupy%20a%20space%20for%20which%20you%20have%20no%20representational%20mandate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20citizen%20is%20constitutionally%20correct%C2%A0in%20this%20complaint%2C%20clearly%20we%20are%20not%C2%A0running%20an%20authentic%20democracy%20but%20a%C2%A0form%20of%20a%20corrupt%20kleptocracy%2C%20wherein%20the%20value%20of%20a%20vote%20may%20be%C2%A0brought%20to%20nought%20by%20politicians%20for%C2%A0whom%20politics%C2%A0is%20no%20longer%20a%20service%20but%20a%20corporate%20career%2C%20permitting%20smart%20corporate%20moves%20from%20one%20company%20to%20a%20more%20lucrative%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilosophical%20individualism%2C%20which%20is%20the%20hallmark%20of%20the%20capitalist%20way%20of%20life%2C%20thus%20becomes%20also%20the%20hallmark%20of%20political%20life%2C%20throwing%20to%20the%20winds%20the%20public%20accountability%20of%20those%20who%20are%20meant%2C%20indeed%20oath-bound%2C%20to%20represent%20and%20further%20the%20needs%20and%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20who%20have%20made%20them%20legislators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20anti-defection%20law%2C%20much%20as%20it%20was%20slated%20to%20bar%20this%20practice%20of%20lucrative%20crossovers%2C%20has%20proved%20woefully%20inadequate%20to%20counter%20the%20cunning%20of%20the%20power-hungry%20offspring%20of%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20may%20therefore%20lend%20its%20usual%20constructive%20ear%20to%20the%20suggestion%20that%20such%20legislators%20who%20wish%20to%20desert%20their%20authorised%20and%20representative%20political%20be