ncomfortable%20with%20my%20family's%20wealth%20and%20figured%20I%20could%20get%20a%20pretty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhighest-paying-tech-jobs-2019-college-grads-gen-z-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-paying%20job%20in%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wouldn't%20need%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20I%20turned%2025%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20decline%20the%20money%3B%20in%20retrospect%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20very%20silly%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20started%20doing%20standup%20comedy%20in%20college%20and%20continued%20doing%20it%20on%20the%20side%20while%20I%20worked.%20After%20about%20four%20years%20of%20working%20as%20a%20product%20manager%2C%20I%20quit%20to%20pursue%20comedy%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20a%20paid%20regular%20at%20some%20comedy%20clubs%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20and%20I've%20also%20done%20some%20festivals.%20I%20do%20around%20five%20shows%20a%20week%20in%20addition%20to%20an%20open%20mic%20or%20two%2C%20and%20I%20produce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donttellcomedy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDon't%20Tell%20Comedy%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20what%20I%20get%20from%20my%20inherited%20investments%20and%20my%20income%20from%20comedy%2C%20my%20money%20has%20remained%20pretty%20stable%20because%20of%20my%20spending%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20make%20many%20large%20purchases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20make%20many%20purchases%20that%20are%20over%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars.%20I%20don't%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-airways-new-york-london-flight-first-class-upgrade-review-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst-class%20plane%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20get%20new%20or%20pricey%20clothing%20very%20often.%20I%20bought%20a%20new%20jacket%20recently%20that%20was%20%24120%20or%20something.%3C%2Fp