.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseefa%2C%2031%2C%20has%20been%20active%20in%20politics%20for%20some%20time%20but%20was%20kept%20away%20from%20parliamentary%20politics%20by%20her%20father%20Zardari%2C%20also%20the%20co-chairperson%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20until%20an%20opportune%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20father's%20inauguration%20as%20the%2014th%20president%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Aseefa%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20First%20Lady%2C%20a%20position%20traditionally%20held%20by%20the%20spouse%20of%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseefa%20submitted%20nomination%20papers%20on%20Sunday%20in%20the%20bye-election%20for%20the%20NA-207%20constituency%20of%20Shaheed%20Benzirabad%20district%20in%20the%20Sindh%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20and%20president%2C%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20won%20the%20seat%20but%20vacated%20it%20after%20becoming%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseefa%20has%20a%20resemblance%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20bombing%20and%20suicide%20attack%20in%202007%20in%20Rawalpindi.%20Aseefa%20was%20then%20a%20teenager%20and%20suffered%20more%20emotionally%20as%20compared%20to%20her%20two%20elder%20siblings%2C%20Bakhtawar%20and%20Bilawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilawal%2C%20a%20former%20foreign%20minister%2C%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20PPP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20the%20reason%20that%20she%20was%20driven%20closer%20to%20her%20father%2C%20who%2C%20after%20becoming%20president%2C%20designated%20her%20the%20First%20Lady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20her%2035-year-old%20brother%20Bilawal%20had%20already%20taken%20over%20the%20party%2C%20Aseefa%20is%20considered%20a%20natural%20heir%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20party%20after%20her%20father%20Zulfiqar%20Ali%20Bhutto%20was%20hanged%20in%201979%20due%20to%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20by-elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2021%2C%20and%20Ase