eshow%2F108613299.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Playing%20Chinese%20Checkers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Backyards%20Not%20in%20Our%20Interest%3A%20CDS%20Anil%20Chauhan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F29130023%2FE2s_e-JVgAQhyXq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EChief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%20on%20Monday%20(March%2018)%20said%20that%20China%20playing%20the%20%E2%80%98game%20of%20checkers%E2%80%99%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20backyard%20will%20not%20be%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20strategic%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDS%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20delivering%20the%20inaugural%20address%20in%20the%20Strategic%20and%20Security%20Dialogue%20on%20%E2%80%98Rise%20of%20China%20and%20Its%20Implications%20for%20the%20World%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Defence%20and%20Strategic%20Studies%20of%20Savitribai%20Phule%20Pune%20University%20along%20with%20the%20Centre%20for%20China%20Analysis%20and%20Strategy%2C%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Centre%20for%20Advanced%20Strategic%20Studies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fcds-anil-chauhan-china-playing-game-of-checkers-in-indias-backyard-9221405%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20important%20security%20challenge%20that%20we%20face%20today%2C%20is%20the%20rising%20fragility%2C%20an%20outcome%20of%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20social%20instability%20in%20our%20immediate%20neighbourhood.%20India%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20only%20island%20of%20stability%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20turmoil%20and%20turbulence.%20Lack%20of%20stable%20governance%20structures%2C%20effective%20law%20enforcement%20can%20create%20safe%20havens%20for%20criminal%20activities%20including%20narcotics%2C%20human%20trafficking%20and%20arms%20smuggling.%20These%20activities%20not%20only%20undermine%20regional%20security%20but%20also%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20destabilise%20our%20security%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20General%20Chauhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstability%20in%20our%20immediate%20and%20extended%20neighbourhood%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20expand%20its%20footprint%20to%20cover%20all%20those%20crucial%20gaps%20that%20other%20people%20can%20fill%20in.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20long%20term%20security%20interest%20that%20China%20plays%20the%20game%20of%20Chinese%20Checkers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20backyards.%20India%20aspires%20and%20must%20become%20the%20first%20responder%20and%20preferred%20security%20partner%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDS%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20challenge%20is%20unsettled%20borders.%20The%20ancient%20frontiers%20of%20India%20started%20taking%20shape%20of%20firm%20borders%20under%20the%20British%20but%20they%20could%20not%20get%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20International%20borders.%20On%20Independence%2C%20thus%20we%20inherited%20disputed%20borders.%20Occupation%20of%20Tibet%20by%20China%20made%20them%20our%20new%20neighbour%20and%20the%20partition%20of%20India%20created%20a%20new%20nation%20that%20thrived%20on%20hostility%20and%20hatred%20towards%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20India%20has%20disputed%20borders%20with%20both%20of%20our%20neighbours.%20Disputes%20followed%20by%20conflicts%20have%20led%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20terms%20like%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20Line%20of%20Control%20and%20Actual%20Ground%20Position%20Line.%20The%20unsettled%20borders%20with%20China%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20China%20will%20remain%20the%20most%20formidable%20challenge%20that%20India%20and%20Indian%20Armed%20forces%20will%20face%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20The%20Armed%20forces%20need%20to%20maintain%20the%20legitimacy