t%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20a%20group%20of%20men%20confronts%20the%20shopkeeper%20over%20playing%20the%20bhajan%20loudly.%20The%20argument%20soon%20turns%20violent%20as%20one%20of%20the%20men%20grabs%20Mukesh's%20collar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20then%20dragged%20him%20out%20of%20the%20shop%20and%20beat%20him%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20assault%20stops%2C%20the%20men%20disperse%20and%20the%20shopkeeper%20returns%20to%20the%20shop%20with%20a%20bloodied%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20playing%20Hanuman%20bhajan.%20Four%20to%20five%20people%20came%20and%20said%20it%20was%20time%20for%20Azaan%20and%20threatened%20to%20beat%20me%20if%20I%20played%20music.%20They%20beat%20me%20and%20threatened%20me%20again%20that%20they%20would%20stab%20me%20with%20a%20knife%2C%26quot%3B%20Mukesh%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20assault%20and%20police%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20still%20on.%20Two%20of%20the%20three%20accused%20are%20Muslims%2C%20while%20one%20is%20Hindu%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20BJP%20President%20BY%20Vijayendra%20attacked%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20and%20urged%20the%20police%20to%20take%20strict%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20government%20accountable%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20Hindus%20and%20Hindu%20establishments%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Siddaramaiah's%20'appeasement%20politics'%20has%20encouraged%20barbarians%20to%20go%20on%20a%20rampage%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20has%20announced%20a%20massive%20program%20at%20Mukesh's%20shop%20at%20noon%20tomorrow%20where%20he%20plans%20to%20play%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20on%20a%20loudspeaker.%C2%A0%20The%20leader%20asked%20BJP%20workers%20to%20ensure%20that%20%26quot%3B