Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20demanding%20the%20protection%20of%20our%20fundamental%20and%20minority%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Catholic%20Bishops%20of%20India%20have%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20that%20the%20government%20officially%20recognises%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20status%20of%20Dalit%20Christians%20and%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20of%20other%20discriminated%20minorities.%20Similarly%2C%20they%20have%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20government%20to%20desist%20from%20any%20attempt%20to%20deprive%20the%20Christian%20tribals%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20politics%20is%20subjected%20to%20the%20hydra-headed%20curse%20of%20populism%2C%20polarisation%2C%20post-truth%20and%20personality%20cult.%20The%20democratic%20institutions%20of%20our%20country%20are%20weakening%2C%20the%20federal%20structure%20is%20being%20relentlessly%20undermined%2C%20the%20media%20has%20been%20co-opted%2C%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20are%20turned%20into%20tools%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20dominant%20class%20to%20harass%20and%20hound%20all%20opposition%2C%20and%20the%20Constitutional%20bodies%20are%20suborned%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ.A.%20Kanthraj%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Archdiocese%20of%20Bangalore%2C%20said%20that%20Machado%20%E2%80%9Chas%20given%20a%20call%20to%20the%20Christian%20Community%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20to%20observe%2C%20Friday%2C%20March%2022%20as%20a%20day%20of%20fasting%20and%20prayer%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20invoke%20God%E2%80%99s%20grace%2C%20strength%20and%20wisdom%20to%20discern%20and%20exercise%20the%20franchise%20responsibly%20and%20dutifully%20for%20the%20good%20of%20our%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710835249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19113826%2F7d49cc_0133531f03864b0181c3abc9cc40cf5dmv2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht