m-international-finance-corp-124031900358_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20investment%20by%20IFC%2C%20World%20Bank's%20private%20sector%20arm%2C%20will%20be%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20subscription%20to%20non-convertible%20debentures%20(NCD)%20issued%20by%20Grasim%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgrasim-industries-secures-rs-1-250-cr-from-international-finance-corp-124031900358_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgrasim-industries-secures-rs-1-250-cr-from-international-finance-corp-124031900358_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgrasim-industries-secures-rs-1-250-cr-from-international-finance-corp-124031900358_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI'm%20Hungry%26quot%3B%3A%20Mumbai%20Start-Up%20Founder%20Strikes%20Gold%20With%20Nvidia%20Backing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sultry%20March%20evening%20in%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20a%20group%20of%20men%20hovers%20anxiously%20at%20the%20back%20gate%20of%20a%20startup%20called%20Yotta%20Data%20Services.%20They%20pace%2C%20pause%2C%20and%20fret.%20It's%20approaching%20midnight%2C%2010%20hours%20late%2C%20when%20a%20truck%20pulls%20up%20with%20the%20precious%20cargo%20they've%20been%20waiting%20for%3A%20semiconductors%20from%20Nvidia%20Corp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20products%20are%20so%20coveted%20because%20they're%20essential%20for%20the%20development%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20technology%20that's%20set%20off%20a%20frenzy%20in%20industries%20around%20the%20world.%20While%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Google%20have%20poured%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20such%20chips%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Yotta%20is%20making%20India's%20largest%20bet%20yet%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Gupta%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20and%20co-founder%2C%20has%20gotten%20a%20jump%20on%20the%20country's%20better-known%20technology%20players%20and%20conglomerates%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20relationship%20he's%20forged%20with%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20Nvidia's%20celebrity%20CEO.%20Yotta%20is%20expected%20to%20feature%20at%20Nvidia's%20developer%20conference%20on%20Monday%20in%20California%2C%20an%20early%20example%20of%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20in%20markets%20beyond%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20ambitious%2C%20I'm%20hungry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gupta%2C%2052.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20bet%20on%20the%20future%20of%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYotta's%20strategy%20is%20to%20offer%20high-performance%20computing%20capabilities%20from%20data%20centers%20in%20India%20so%20the%20country's%20corporations%2C%20startups%20and%20researchers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20develop%20their%20own%20AI%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20chips%2C%20the%20most%20advanced%20on%20the%20market%2C%20are%20essential%20for%20training%20large%20language%20models%20and%20building%20applications%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20Microsoft%20Corp.'s%20coding%20assistant%2C%20GitHub%20Copilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20figures%20he's%20got%20an%20edge%20over%20cloud%20computing%20services%20outside%20the%20country%20because%20of%20latency%20issues%2C%20and%20he%20vows%20to%20offer%20the%20least%20expensive%20access%20to%20Nvidia%20AI%20chips%20in%20the%20world.%20He's%20even%20considering%20letting%20Indian%20startups%20with%20tight%20budgets%20give%20him%20equity%20instead%20of%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemand%20is%20on%20his%20side.%20The%20global%20AI%20market%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20from%20%24168.5%20billion%20in%202022%20to%20over%20%242%20trillion%20by%202032%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Spherical%20Insights%20%26amp%3B%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20gold%20rush%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Stacy%20Rasgon%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Sanford%20C.%20Bernstein.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20the%20early%20days%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20companies%20just%20can't%20buy%20enough%20of%20this%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20era%20got%20off%20to%20a%20rocky%20start%20this%20month%20in%20India.%20The%20country's%20customs%20officials%20were%20flummoxed%20by%20the%20unusually%20high%20value%20of%20the%20Nvidia%20chips%20that%20Yotta%20had%20purchased%2C%20leading%20to%20requisitions%20of%20additional%20paperwork%20and%20bureaucratic%20approval.%20Back%20in%20his%20data%20center%20outside%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20paced%20the%20marble%20floors%20of%20the%20lobby%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20a%20day%2C%20working%20the%20phones%20to%20get%20his%20chips%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delivery%20truck%20finally%20pulled%20up%20and%20workers%20unloaded%20the%20first%20of%20more%20than%204%2C000%20H100%20chips%20that%20Yotta%20ordered%20from%20Nvidia.%20The%20beefy%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20or%20GPUs%2C%20run%20%2430%2C000%20to%20%2440%2C000%20each%20and%20are%20called%20Hoppers%20in%20a%20nod%20to%20computer%20science%20pioneer%20Grace%20Hopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delivery%20was%20a%20religious%20experience%20for%20Mr%20Gupta%2C%20quite%20literally.%20A%20priest%20adorned%20the%20boxes%20with%20red%20vermilion%20marks%20and%20strings%20of%20yellow%20chrysanthemum%20flowers%2C%20while%20hymns%20in%20ancient%20Sanskrit%20filled%20the%20night%20air.%20A%20camera-carrying%20drone%20recorded%20as%20Mr%20Gupta%20symbolically%20smashed%20a%20coconut%20on%20the%20floor%20near%20the%20truck.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20dream%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20amid%20exploding%20party%20poppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYotta's%20haul%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20which%20will%20reach%20about%2020%2C000%20by%20June%2C%20isn't%20huge%20by%20global%20standards.%20Tech%20giants%20like%20Microsoft%20Corp.%20purchase%20them%20by%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%2C%20and%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.'s%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20get%20350%2C000%20H100s%20by%20year-end.%20Still%2C%20Nvidia's%20supply%20is%20far%20short%20of%20demand%20so%20CEO%20Huang%20has%20to%20calibrate%20allocations%20as%20corporate%20titans%20and%20heads%20of%20state%20press%20for%20allotments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20getting%20special%20attention.%20In%20September%2C%20Huang%20met%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20said%20he%20would%20prioritize%20any%20orders%20from%20data%20center%20operators%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20data%2C%20you%20have%20the%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20AI%20markets%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20got%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Nvidia%20team%20asking%20him%20if%20he%20could%20meet%20the%20CEO%20in%20the%20western%20city%20of%20Pune.%20Though%20it%20was%20late%20evening%20and%20the%20meeting%20would%20be%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20quickly%20agreed.%20He%20jumped%20in%20his%20car%20and%20drove%20three%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20through%20the%20night%20for%20the%20confab.%20It%20was%20a%20demonstration%20that%20Yotta%20would%20go%20above%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20has%20serious%20bona%20fides%20in%20the%20field.%20He's%20been%20working%20for%20decades%20on%20data%20center%20businesses%20and%20co-founded%20Yotta%20in%202019%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20real%20estate%20billionaire%20Niranjan%20Hiranandani.%20As%20a%20cloud%20computing%20operator%2C%20Yotta%20offers%20companies%20like%20Wells%20Fargo%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20access%20to%20data%20storage%20and%20computing%20power%20they%20can%20scale%20up%20or%20down%20as%20needed%2C%20without%20buying%20and%20installing%20their%20own%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Group%20and%20Reliance%20Industries%20Ltd%2C%20two%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20conglomerates%2C%20plan%20to%20develop%20AI%20infrastructure%20too%2C%20but%20have%20yet%20to%20order%20Nvidia's%20most%20advanced%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Nvidia%20spokeswoman%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20Yotta's%20order%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20more%20will%20be%20revealed%20this%20week.%20Mr%20Gupta%20is%20speaking%20at%20Nvidia%20GPU%20Technology%20Conference%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20told%20Huang%20will%20discuss%20Yotta%20during%20his%20keynote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20for%20the%20attention%20is%20a%20global%20imbalance%20in%20AI.%20If%20the%20technology%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20virtually%20every%20industry%2C%20as%20Huang%20and%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20argue%2C%20then%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20Indonesia%20or%20Turkey%20are%20at%20risk%20without%20access.%20In%20India%2C%20that%20could%20stymie%20scientific%20research%2C%20startup%20development%20and%2C%20more%20broadly%2C%20Modi's%20ambitions%20to%20create%20a%20technology%20superpower.%20%26quot%3BGPU%20disparity%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20increasingly%20popular%20term%20for%20the%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCountries%20who%20don't%20have%20their%20own%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20models%20will%20woefully%20lose%20the%20AI%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Umakant%20Soni%2C%20co-founder%20of%20a%20nonprofit%20AI%20and%20robotics%20research%20park%20called%20ARTPARK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20sees%20a%20clear%20need%20to%20develop%20India-built%20AI%20models%2C%20trained%20with%20local%20languages%20and%20cultural%20diversity.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20needs%20sovereign%20AI%2C%20India%20needs%20sovereign%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeopolitics%20is%20helping%20his%20case.%20Rising%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20have%20led%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20levy%20sweeping%20controls%20over%20the%20export%20of%20technologies%20to%20its%20geopolitical%20rival%2C%20including%20the%20very%20H100%20Nvidia%20chips%20Yotta%20is%20buying.%20Cloud%20providers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20also%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20a%20key%20US%20lawmaker%20urged%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20to%20probe%20the%20Chinese%20connections%20of%20Abu%20Dhabi-based%20AI%20firm%20G42.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20figures%20he%20can%20supply%20Indian%20customers%20and%20others%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20Yotta%20already%20has%20half-dozen%20data%20centers%20in%20four%20Indian%20cities%2C%20and%20a%20new%20one%20opening%20in%20India's%20northeast.%20The%20entrepreneur%20named%20his%20company%20after%20the%20number%20eight%20in%20ancient%20Greek%2C%20representing%20one%20septillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20playing%20a%20bit%20of%20catchup%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nruthya%20Madappa%2C%20a%20partner%20with%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%203one4%20Capital.%20%26quot%3BBut%20because%20of%20the%20talent%20base%2C%20we%20see%20the%20catchup%20being%20very%2C%20very%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven-floor%20data%20center%20outside%20Mumbai%20is%20surrounded%20by%20electric%20fences%2C%20equipped%20with%20850%20cameras%20and%20includes%20seven%20layers%20of%20security.%20Mammoth%20diesel%20storage%20tanks%20hold%20enough%20fuel%20to%20run%20the%20facilities%20for%2048%20hours%20if%20the%20power%20goes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta's%20partnership%20with%20Nvidia%20mandates%20such%20rigid%20protocols%2C%20along%20with%20stringent%20specs%20for%20building%20the%20AI%20cloud%20business.%20He's%20sealed%20off%20the%20facility's%20entire%20sixth%20floor%20for%20that%20purpose.%20An%20Nvidia%20team%20will%20arrive%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20to%20get%20the%20network%20up%20and%20running%2C%20with%20a%20target%20of%20starting%20operations%20in%20mid-May.%20Mr%20Gupta%20calls%20the%20first%20H100%20cloud%20service%20'Shakti'%2C%20the%20Hindi%20word%20for%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20he's%20sold%20out%20capacity%20for%20the%20day%20his%20network%20goes%20live%2C%20and%20has%20a%20waiting%20list%20of%20companies%20from%20India%20and%20beyond.%20Gupta%20is%20already%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20next%20delivery%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20more%20than%2016%2C000%20scheduled%20for%20June.%20He'll%20do%20at%20least%20one%20thing%20differently%20though%3A%20hire%20guards%20since%20the%20value%20of%20the%20shipment%20could%20run%20into%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecurity%3F!%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20that!%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gupta.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20want%20these.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710834780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fugjl8u9o_yotta-nvidia-bloomberg_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fim-hungry-mumbai-start-up-founder-strikes-gold-with-nvidia-backing-5267641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yotta's%20products%20are%20so%20coveted%20because%20they're%20essential%20for%20the%20development%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20technology%20that's%20set%20off%20a%20frenzy%20in%20industries%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fim-hungry-mumbai-start-up-founder-strikes-gold-with-nvidia-backing-5267641%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fim-hungry-mumbai-start-up-founder-strikes-gold-with-nvidia-backing-5267641%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fim-hungry-mumbai-start-up-founder-strikes-gold-with-nvidia-ba