%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68603469.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68603469.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Mocked%20About%20Net%20Worth%20As%20He%20Struggles%20To%20Pay%20%24464%20Million%20Bond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20earlier%20remarks%20on%20his%20wealth%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20and%20widespread%20mockery%20after%20his%20attorneys%20stated%20that%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20funds%20to%20pay%20the%20penalty%20associated%20with%20a%20recent%20court%20judgment.%20The%20lawyers%20said%20that%20he%20is%20having%20%26quot%3Binsurmountable%20difficulties%26quot%3B%20getting%20a%20bond%20to%20pay%20the%20%24%20464%20million%20civil%20fraud%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Arthur%20Engoron%20found%20Mr%20Trump%20guilty%20in%20February%20of%20using%20fraudulent%20financial%20statements%20to%20conduct%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20business%2C%20exaggerating%20his%20real%20estate%20holdings%20and%20inflating%20his%20wealth.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20%24464%20million%20in%20disgorgement%20and%20interest%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EABC%20News.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20judge%20ordered%20the%2045th%20US%20President%20to%20pay%20%24355%20million%20plus%20interest%20while%20his%20sons%20Eric%20and%20Don%20Jr%20were%20told%20to%20hand%20over%20more%20than%20%244%20million%20each.%20According%20to%20the%20lawyers%2C%20the%20punishment%20was%20too%20harsh%20and%20%26quot%3Benforcing%20an%20impossible%20bond%20requirement%20as%20a%20condition%20of%20appeal%20would%20inflict%20manifest%20irreparable%20injury%20on%20defendants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20only%20two%20weeks%20after%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20whose%20net%20worth%20was%20assessed%20by%20Forbes%20to%20be%20around%20%242.6%20million%20in%20September%202023%2C%20told%20Fox%20News%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20wealthy.%20I'm%20free%20to%20act%20whatever%20I%20like.%26quot%3B%20Additionally%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Bworry%26quot%3B%20about%20money%20or%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20has%20caused%20a%20huge%20uproar%20on%20social%20media%20with%20many%20criticising%20comments%20regarding%20his%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20else%20find%20it%20odd%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20testified%20(and%20affirmed%20with%20banks)%20that%20he%20had%20a%20liquid%20net%20worth%20close%20to%20%241B%20but%20now%20can't%20afford%20bond%20for%20half%20of%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20bright%20side%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20he%20won't%20be%20impacted%20by%20President%20Biden's%20proposed%20billionaires%20tax.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSelf-described%20billionaire%20Trump%20hits%20a%20cash-flow%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGreat%20news%2C%20he'll%20have%20no%20money%20for%20the%20election%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20what%20he%20said%20in%20the%20hall%20when%20he%20came%20out%20and%20talked%20at%20the%20fraud%20trial%20he%20said%20'money%20is%20not%20a%20problem'%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20he%20was%20a%20billionaire%3F%20%C2%A0So%20is%20he%20lying%20to%20the%20public%20or%20the%20Court%3F%26quot%3B%20added%20an%20X%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710833700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fae6khilo_donald-trump_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-mocked-about-net-worth-as-he-struggles-to-pay-464-million-bond-5267537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20comes%20only%20two%20weeks%20after%20Mr%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20wealthy.%20I'm%20free%20to%20act%20whatever%20I%20like.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-mocked-about-net-worth-as-he-struggles-to-pay-464-million-bond-5267537%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-mocked-about-net-worth-as-he-struggles-to-pay-464-million-bond-5267537%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-mocked-about-net-worth-as-he-struggles-to-pay-464-million-bond-5267537%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Counter%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Factor%2C%20BJP's%20Pick%20Is%20His%20Estranged%20Cousin%20Raj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20push%20to%20maximise%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20tally%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20likely%20to%20resurrect%20Raj%20Thackeray's%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%20from%20political%20oblivion.%20Determined%20to%20blunt%20the%20challenge%20by%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20his%20estranged%20cousin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20Thackeray%20reached%20Delhi%20last%20night%20and%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%2C%20apparently%20to%20discuss%20his%20party's%20possible%20entry%20into%20the%20NDA.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20told%20to%20come%20to%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20came.%20Let's%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MNS%20chief%20said%20on%20arriving%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20He%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20media%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMNS%20leader%20Sandeep%20Deshpande%20has%20said%20they%20will%20share%20details%20of%20the%20meeting%20soon.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20will%20be%20for%20the%20greater%20good%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Marathis%2C%20Hindutva%20and%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MNS%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20wants%20three%20seats%20-%20South%20Mumbai%2C%20Shirdi%20and%20Nashik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20BJP%20Wooing%20MNS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20MNS%20lies%20in%20how%20Maharashtra's%20political%20landscape%20has%20transformed%20since%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20In%20the%20last%20general%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20contested%20the%20polls%20together.%20The%20alliance%20decimated%20rivals%20and%20won%2041%20out%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats.%20Months%20later%2C%20it%20clinched%20another%20victory%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%20But%20differences%20over%20sharing%20power%20led%20to%20the%20Sena%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20NDA.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20But%20more%20drama%20was%20to%20follow.%20In%202022%2C%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20a%20mutiny%20that%20toppled%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government.%20Mr%20Shinde%20then%20joined%20ranks%20with%20BJP%20to%20take%20over.%20In%20the%20legal%20battle%20that%20followed%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20lost%20his%20party's%20name%20and%20symbol%20and%20his%20camp%20was%20named%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strikingly%20similar%20manner%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20split%20after%20a%20rebellion%20led%20by%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20The%20NCP%20veteran%2C%20too%2C%20lost%20his%20party's%20name%20and%20symbol%20and%20now%20leads%20a%20faction%20named%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar).%20So%20from%20a%20straight%20contest%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Lok%20Sabha%20fight%20is%20now%20a%20multipronged%20battle%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20NCP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20camps%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20a%20tricky%20terrain%20and%20it%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20take%20chances%20in%20the%20politically-significant%20state%20that%20is%20critical%20to%20the%20BJP's%20target%20to%20win%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20So%20to%20counter%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20factor%2C%20it%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20his%20cousin%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMNS%20Eyes%20Big%20Return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202006%20after%20Raj%20Thackeray%20walked%20out%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20over%20differences%20with%20cousin%20Uddhav%2C%20the%20MNS%20recorded%20its%20best%20electoral%20performance%20in%20the%202009%20state%20polls%20when%20it%20won%2013%20seats.%20In%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20it%20emerged%20as%20the%20big%20loser%2C%20winning%20just%20one%20seat.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20too%2C%20its%20tally%20remained%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%20has%20struggled%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20political%20limelight%20with%20often%20controversial%20remarks%20in%20the%20media.%20When%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%2C%20he%20went%20all%20out%20against%20his%20estranged%20cousin%2C%20holding%20him%20responsible%20for%20the%20party's%20crisis.%20He%20has%20also%20warmed%20up%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20with%20the%20two%20leaders%20meeting%20on%20several%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20the%20BJP%20are%20finalised%2C%20the%20MNS%20may%20get%20a%20shot%20at%20reviving%20its%20political%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710833460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fgcqvjrdg_raj-thackeray_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraj-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-mns-bjp-to-counter-one-thackeray-bjp-reaches-out-to-another-thackeray-5267283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20push%20to%20maximise%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20tally%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20likely%20to%20resurrect%20Raj%20Thackeray's%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%20from%20political%20oblivion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraj-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-mns-bjp-to-counter-one-thackeray-bjp-reaches-out-to-another-thackeray-5267283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraj-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-mns-bjp-to-counter-one-thackeray-bjp-reaches-out-to-another-thackeray-5267283%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraj-thackeray-uddhav-thackeray-mns-bjp-to-counter-one-thackeray-bjp-reaches-out-to-another-thackeray-5267283%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%3A%20Government%20Reveals%20Religion-Wise%20Break-Up%20of%20NRC%20Exclusions%20for%20the%20First%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20the%20government%20has%20revealed%20details%20by%20religion%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20or%20NRC%2C%20conducted%20under%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20published%20on%20August%2031%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20said%20that%20of%20the%2016%20lakh%20names%20excluded%20from%20the%20final%20draft%20of%20NRC%2C%20there%20were%20seven%20lakh%20Muslims.%20He%20said%20there%20were%20five%20lakh%20Bengali%20Hindus%2C%20two%20lakh%20Assamese%20Hindus%20(caste%20Axomiya%20and%20Koch-Rajbongshi)%20and%201.5%20lakh%20Gorkhas%20on%20the%20list.%20He%20did%20not%20reveal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1065331%2F7-lakh-muslims-5-lakh-bengali-hindus-left-out-of-assam-nrc-says-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Ewho%20the%20remaining%203.5%20lakh%20persons%20were%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20made%20claims%20on%20numbers%20that%20he%20thinks%20will%20apply%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20fresh%20rules%20issued%20for%20the%20contentious%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20recently.%20He%20is%20reported%20as%20telling%20News%20Live%2C%20a%20local%20TV%20channel%2C%20that%20only%20%E2%80%9C3%20to%206%20lakh%20people%20will%20apply%20with%20CAA%20and%20not%2020%2C%2018%20or%2015%20lakhs%20or%201.5%20crores%2C%20which%20some%20people%20are%20claiming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAA%20%E2%80%9Cfiasco%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Sarma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20is%20battling%20growing%20resentment%20over%20CAA%20rules%20in%20Assam.%20Opposition%20and%20other%20civil%20society%20groups%20are%20annoyed%20over%20what%20they%20think%20would%20be%20an%20attack%20on%20indigenous%20culture%20of%20Assam%20if%20the%20law%20to%20fast-track%20citizenship%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpersecuted%E2%80%9D%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%C2%A0%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20was%20to%20be%20implemented.%20The%20amended%20law%20was%20passed%20in%20December%202019%2C%20and%20led%20to%20severe%20protests%20and%20outrage%20in%20Assam%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20speculate%20that%20the%20Act%20would%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfiasco%E2%80%9D%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20it%20would%20see%20the%20lowest%20numbers%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%203%20to%206%20lakh%20people%20will%20apply%20with%20CAA%20and%20not%2020%2C%2018%20or%2015%20lakhs%20or%201.5%20crores%2C%20which%20some%20people%20are%20claiming.%20It%20can%20be%2010%25%20more%20or%20less%20but%20not%20more%20than%206%20lakhs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20cited%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-3-6-lakh-people-may-apply-under-caa-in-assam-not-1-5-crore-himanta-biswa-sarma-101710777297588.html%5C%22%3Etelling%20the%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20CAA%20rules%20were%20announced%20last%20week%20and%20by%20April%2019%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20around%2040%20days.%20This%20will%20be%20enough%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20actual%20scenario.%2013%20Hindu%20families%20in%20Gujarat%20have%20already%20been%20granted%20citizenship%20with%20CAA%20but%20in%20Assam%2C%20not%20many%20people%20have%20applied%20till%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20many%20families%2C%20especially%20Hindu%20Bengalis%2C%20entered%20Assam%20from%20Bangladesh%20after%20March%2025%2C%201971%2C%20the%20cut-off%20date%20for%20being%20entitled%20to%20get%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20of%20them%20returned%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20these%20families%20were%20denied%20ration%20cards%20by%20the%20authorities%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20they%20only%20had%20one%20document%2C%20the%20refugee%20registration%20cards%20issued%20by%20border%20authorities.%20But%20Prateek%20Hajela%20(former%20state%20coordinator%20of%20NRC)%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20these%20cards%20in%20the%20NRC%20updation%20process%2C%20due%20to%20this%2C%20many%20names%20were%20excluded%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Assam%20government%20went%20after%20Prateek%20Hajela%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20an%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Assam-Meghalaya%20cadre%2C%20and%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fassam-cm-orders-probe-against-former-nrc-coordinator-prateek-hajela-for-alleged-irregularities-assam-nrc-prateekhajela-illegalimmigrants-probe-corruption-101681366646111.html%5C%22%3Eis%20set%20to%20face%20a%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20committed%20while%20updating%20the%20register%20that%20was%20aimed%20to%20detect%20undocumented%20persons%20who%20could%20be%20present%20