ch%20had%20been%20widely%20anticipated.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETOKYO%20(AP)%20%E2%80%94%20Japan's%20central%20bank%20raised%20its%20benchmark%20interest%20rate%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2017%20years%2C%20ending%20a%20longstanding%20policy%20of%20negative%20rates%20meant%20to%20boost%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short-term%20rate%20was%20raised%20to%20a%20range%20of%200%20to%200.1%25%20from%20minus%200.1%25%20at%20a%20policy%20meeting%20that%20confirmed%20expectations%20of%20a%20shift%20away%20from%20ultra-lax%20monetary%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20rate%20hike%20since%20February%202007.%20The%20negative%20interest%20rate%20policy%2C%20combined%20with%20other%20measures%20to%20inject%20money%20into%20the%20economy%20and%20keep%20borrowing%20costs%20low%2C%20%26quot%3Bhave%20fulfilled%20their%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20an%20inflation%20target%20of%202%25%20that%20it%20used%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20whether%20Japan%20had%20finally%20escaped%20deflationary%20tendencies.%20But%20it%20had%20remained%20cautious%20about%20%26quot%3Bnormalizing%26quot%3B%20monetary%20policy%2C%20or%20ending%20negative%20borrowing%20rates%2C%20even%20after%20data%20showed%20inflation%20at%20about%20that%20rate%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20supporting%20the%20shift%3A%20Japanese%20companies%20have%20announced%20relatively%20robust%20wage%20hikes%20for%20this%20year's%20round%20of%20negotiations%20with%20trade%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWages%20and%20profits%20at%20companies%20were%20improving%2C%20the%20Bank%20of%20Japan%20said%2C%20in%20releasing%20its%20latest%20decision%2C%20referring%20to%20%26quot%3Banecdotal%26quot%3B%20accounts%20as%20well%20as%20data%20it%20had%20gathered%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan's%20economy%20has%20recovered%20moderately%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20scant%20reaction%20in%20markets%20to%20the%20decision%2C%20which%20had%20been%20widely%20anticipated.%20Tokyo's%20benchmark%20Nikkei%20225%20index%20gained%200.4%25%2C%20while%20the%20dollar%20was%20steady%20at%20about%20150%20yen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fthe-bank-of-japan-fumio-kishida-tokyo-business-75630c57b21f95c1d4e38e4c5f911165%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20Japan%20Chief%20Kazuo%20Ueda%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20repeatedly%20said%20the%20bank%20would%20review%20its%20negative%20rate%20and%20other%20easing%20measures%20if%20the%202%20percent%20inflation%20target%20was%20met%20and%20was%20accompanied%20by%20wage%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20central%20bank's%20policy%20is%20quite%20different%20from%20those%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffederal-reserve-inflation-prices-interest-rates-cuts-fe4b77c6b8901fb5d8b50e891dafbe34%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Federal%20Reserve%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20European%20Central%20Bank.%20Both%20have%20been%20moving%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates%20after%20rapidly%20raising%20them%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bank%20of%20Japan%20has%20kept%20borrowing%20costs%20extremely%20low%20for%20many%20years%20to%20encourage%20Japanese%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20to%20spend%20and%20invest%20to%20help%20sustain%20stronger%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fjapan-economy-2023-gdp-893d53deba654c4924e4924f0b321cc5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20recently%20became%20the%20world's%20fourth-biggest%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20slipping%20behind%20Germany%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20nominal%20gross%20domestic%20product%2C%20or%20GDP.%20The%20U.S.%20economy%20is%20the%20largest%2C%20followed%20by%20China%2C%20which%20overtook%20Japan%20over%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBOJ%20officials%20say%20they%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20inflation%20is%20based%20on%20domestic%20factors%20that%20can%20sustain%20higher%20wages%2C%20not%20external%20ones.%20Analysts%20expect%20the%20Bank%20of%20Japan%20to%20continue%20to%20move%20slowly%20on%20further%20raising%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultra-lax%20monetary%20policy%20also%20included%20huge%20injections%20of%20money%20into%20the%20economy%20through%20purchases%20of%20Japanese%20government%20bonds%20and%20other%20assets.%20The%20bank%20said%20the%20BOJ%20would%20continue%20with%20those%20government%20bond%20purchases%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20about%206%20trillion%20yen%20(%2440.2%20billion)%2C%20and%20adjust%20quickly%20depending%20on%20economic%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20discontinued%20or%20gave%20timelines%20for%20ending%20purchases%20of%20real%20estate%20investment%20trusts%20and%20other%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultra-lax%20monetary%20policy%20that%20Ueda's%20predecessor%2C%20Haruhiko%20Kuroda%2C%20put%20in%20place%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20was%20designed%20to%20establish%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bvirtuous%20cycle%26quot%3B%20of%20inflationary%20expectations%20that%20would%20lead%20people%20to%20spend%20more%20both%20because%20borrowing%20costs%20were%20low%20and%20because%20they%20feared%20prices%20would%20rise%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20meant%20to%20counter%20a%20spell%20of%20deflationary%20trends%20where%20people%20held%20back%20on%20purchases%20in%20hopes%20of%20lower%20prices%2C%20which%20led%20companies%20to%20invest%20less%20and%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bank%20of%20Japan%20said%20in%20its%20assessment%20of%20the%20economy%20that%20the%20current%20recovery%20was%20based%20partly%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bmaterialization%20of%20pent-up%20demand%26quot%3B%20even%20as%20global%20demand%20has%20weakened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20noted%20that%20industrial%20production%20was%20stagnant%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20cutbacks%20by%20automakers.%20Housing%20investment%20was%20relatively%20weak%20and%20government%20spending%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20or%20less%20flat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConcerning%20risks%20to%20the%20outlook%2C%20there%20are%20extremely%20high%20uncertainties%20surrounding%20Japan's%20economic%20activity%20and%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-central-bank-raises-interest-rates-17-years-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710831302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f936534af076d3cf918bd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-central-bank-raises-interest-rates-17-years-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Japanese%20central%20bank's%20policy%20is%20quite%20different%20from%20those%20of%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20and%20the%20European%20Central%20Bank%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20been%20moving%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Yuri%20Kageyama)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-central-bank-raises-interest-rates-17-years-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDeeply%20Concerned%20About%20Impact%20Of%20CAA%20On%20Muslims%20In%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20Senator%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20senator%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20Indian%20government%20notifying%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20saying%20that%20as%20the%20US-India%20relationship%20deepens%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20the%20cooperation%20is%20based%20on%20shared%20values%20of%20protecting%20human%20rights%20of%20all%2C%20regardless%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20implemented%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20last%20week%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20citizenship%20to%20undocumented%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20came%20out%20with%20a%20press%20statement%20to%20say%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20need%20not%20worry%20as%20the%20CAA%20will%20not%20impact%20their%20citizenship%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20community%20which%20enjoys%20equal%20rights%20as%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20concerned%20by%20the%20Indian%20government's%20decision%20to%20notify%20its%20controversial%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20particularly%20the%20law's%20potential%20ramifications%20on%20India's%20Muslim%20community.%20Making%20matters%20worse%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20being%20pushed%20during%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan%2C%26quot%3B%20Senator%20Ben%20Cardin%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20powerful%20Senate%20Foreign%20Relations%20Committee%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20US-India%20relationship%20deepens%2C%20it%20is%20critically%20important%20that%20our%20cooperation%20is%20based%20on%20our%20shared%20values%20of%20protecting%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20all%20persons%2C%20regardless%20of%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20had%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20notifying%20of%20the%20CAA%20and%20said%20that%20respect%20for%20religious%20freedom%20and%20equal%20treatment%20under%20the%20law%20for%20all%20communities%20are%20fundamental%20democratic%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20sharply%20rebuked%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20for%20its%20criticism%20of%20the%20CAA%20and%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bmisinformed%20and%20unwarranted.%26quot%3B%20In%20separate%20statements%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Policy%20Research%20and%20Advocacy%20Collective%20(HinduPACT)%20and%20the%20Global%20Hindu%20Heritage%20Foundation%20supported%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20provides%20expedited%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20Hindu%2C%20Christian%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%20and%20Parsi%20minorities%20from%20India's%20neighbouring%20countries.%20It%20underscores%20India's%20dedication%20to%20safeguarding%20individuals%20and%20families%20against%20religious%20persecution%2C%20resonating%20with%20global%20humanitarian%20principles%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20does%20not%20impact%20any%20citizen%20of%20India.%20The%20characterisation%20of%20this%20law%20as%20being%20non-secular%20is%20unfounded.%20Hindu%20minority%20is%20discriminated%20against%20and%20decimated%20in%20India's%20neighbourhood.%20As%20Americans%2C%20we%20are%20disappointed%20that%20instead%20of%20standing%20for%20American%20values%20and%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20persecuted%2C%20our%20government%20has%20chosen%20to%20oppose%20this%20humanitarian%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ajay%20Shah%2C%20founder%20and%20co-convenor%20of%20HinduPACT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepti%20Mahajan%2C%20co-convenor%20of%20HinduPACT%2C%20said%20it%20is%20shocking%20to%20see%20the%20lack%20of%20empathy%20towards%20the%20plight%20of%20little%20girls%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%20and%20Christian%20minority%20communities%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%2C%20BBC%20and%20APPG%20reports%2C%20on%20average%2C%201%2C000%20girls%20a%20year%2C%20as%20little%20as%2010%20years%20old%2C%20get%20abducted%2C%20converted%2C%20and%20become%20victims%20of%20sex%20slavery%20and%20forced%20marriages%20in%20Pakistan.%20Instead%20of%20calling%20out%20the%20government%20of%20Pakistan%20for%20its%20complicity%20in%20this%20ongoing%20heartbreaking%20act%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20seeks%20to%20criticise%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20effort%20to%20help%20these%20innocent%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Global%20Hindu%20Heritage%20Foundation's%20V%20S%20Naipaul%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20addresses%20the%20plight%20of%20minorities%2C%20who%20are%20facing%20brutalities%2C%20persecution%2C%20forced%20conversion%2C%20murders%2C%20rapes%2C%20and%20all%20kinds%20of%20atrocities%20in%20our%20neighbouring%20Islamic%20countries%2C%20where%20the%20idea%20of%20secularism%2C%20peace%20and%20humanity%20just%20cannot%20survive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710831000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fojm7jce_senator-ben-cardin_625x300_03_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeeply-concerned-about-impact-of-caa-on-muslims-in-india-us-senator-5267318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20American%20senator%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20Indian%20government%20notifying%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20saying%20that%20as%20the%20US-India%20relationship%20deepens%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20the%20cooperation%20is%20based%20on%20shared%20values.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeeply-concerned-about-impact-of-caa-on-muslims-in-india-us-senator-5267318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeeply-concerned-about-impact-of-caa-on-muslims-in-india-us-senator-5267318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeeply-concerned-about-impact-of-caa-on-muslims-in-india-us-senator-5267318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US-Philippines%20alliance%20is%20%E2%80%98ironclad%E2%80%99-%20Blinken%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710830930000%2C%