n-national-federations-suspension-lifted-by-world-body-with-immediate-effect%5C%22%3Edissolved%20the%20ad-hoc%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20responsible%20for%20managing%20the%20daily%20affairs%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20handing%20back%20charge%20to%20the%20governing%20body%20elected%20in%20December%2C%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Ffield%2F1065395%2Fwrestling-ioa-dissolves-ad-hoc-committee-elected-body-to-take-charge-of-national-federation%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20elected%20body%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-suspend-sanjay-singh-gonda%5C%22%3Esuspended%20days%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20WFI%20president%20on%20December%2021%20for%20being%20%E2%80%9Cin%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office%20bearers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ad-hoc%20committee%2C%20during%20its%20tenure%2C%20conducted%20national%20trials%20for%20both%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20categories%20to%20finalise%20the%20Indian%20team%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Asian%20Wrestling%20Championships%20and%20World%20Olympic%20qualifiers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20to%20dissolve%20the%20Adhoc%20Committee%20comes%20in%20light%20of%20the%20lifting%20of%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20by%20the%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20and%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20Selection%20Trials%20by%20the%20Adhoc%20Committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20IOA%20as%20per%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20release%20from%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Ffield%2F1063664%2Fwrestling-indian-national-federations-suspension-lifted-by-world-body-with-immediate-effect%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20ad-hoc%20committee%2C%20Singh%20is%20set%20to%20lead%20wrestling%20activities%20in%20India.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20former%20WFI%20President%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Eaccused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20several%20women%20wrestlers%20and%20faced%20massive%20protests%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20received%20severe%20backlash%20with%20Olympic%20medalist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20announcing%20that%20she%20was%20giving%20up%20the%20sport%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20has%20instructed%20WFI%20to%20appoint%20a%20Safeguarding%20Committee%20to%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20abuse%20and%20harassment.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20federation%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20establish%20an%20Athletes%20Commission%20to%20ensure%20athlete%20representation%20in%20decision-making%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20instructed%20by%20the%20UWW%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20WFI%20appoint%20a%20Safeguarding%20Committee%20%2F%20Officer%20at%20the%20earliest%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20abuse%20and%20harassment%20and%20to%20ensure%20adherence%20to%20all%20rules%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20guidelines%20set%20forth%20by%20the%20UWW%20and%20other%20relevant%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IOA%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20wrestling%20body%20has%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20repay%20the%20loan%20provided%20by%20the%20IOA%20to%20the%20now-disbanded%20ad-hoc%20committee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20being%20elected%2C%20Singh%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20Under-15%20and%20Under-20%20nationals%20will%20take%20place%20at%20Nandini%20Nagar%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gonda%20before%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20which%20the%20sports%20ministry%20had%20called%20%E2%80%9Chasty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGonda%20is%20also%20understood%20to%20be%20Brij%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20sports%20ministry%20had%20slammed%20the%20federation%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20regard%20for%20norms.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20of%20the%20Federation%20is%20being%20run%20from%20the%20premises%20controlled%20by%20former%20office%20bearers%E2%80%A6Which%20is%20also%20alleged%20premises%20wherein%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20the%20players%20have%20been%20alleged%20and%20present%20the%20court%20is%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20sports%20ministry%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-suspend-sanjay-singh-gonda%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Singh%2C%2012%20of%20the%2015%20posts%20in%20which%20elections%20were%20held%20were%20taken%20up%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20was%20accused%20of%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20at%20least%20seven%20women%20wrestlers.%20While%20the%20police%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20him%20and%20he%20continues%20in%20his%20position%20as%20MP%2C%20he%20was%20removed%20as%20the%20WFI%20head%20after%20prolonged%20protests%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20wrestlers%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710829818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24114233%2FGCFyV08WwAAuJDh.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fioa-dissolves-ad-hoc-body-wfi-led-by-brij-bhushans-close-aid-sanjay-singh-back-in-charge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20newly%20elected%20body%20had%20been%20suspended%20days%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20appointment%20as%20WFI%20president%20for%20being%20%E2%80%9Cin%20complete%20control%20of%20forme