ct%20that%C2%A0the%20RSS%20has%20used%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cdisruptive%20forces%E2%80%9D%20to%20characterise%20the%20farmers%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20who%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfighting%20against%20the%20corporatisation%20of%20the%20agriculture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20Hindutva%20terrorism%20that%20is%20acting%20as%20the%20most%20disruptive%20internal%20threat%20to%20the%20unity%20and%20diversity%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claimed%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20aligned%20with%20politics%20that%20has%20favoured%C2%A0international%20finance%20capital%20and%20big%20business%20and%20which%20threatens%20Indian%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRSS%20should%20not%20forget%20its%20history%20of%20collusion%20with%20the%20imperialist%20forces%20and%20with%20imperialist%20agencies%20like%20the%20CIA.%20CIA%20agent%20J.A.%20Curran%2C%20who%20enjoyed%20unusual%20access%20to%20the%20top%20brass%20of%20RSS%20from%201949%20to%201951%2C%20in%20his%20book%20had%20identified%20RSS%20as%20a%20tool%20that%20would%20help%20the%20imperialist%20block%20led%20by%20the%20USA%20to%20contain%20the%20militant%20peasant%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20movement%20in%20independent%20India.%20By%20demonising%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20against%20corporatisation%2C%20RSS%20is%20showing%20its%20support%20for%20imperialist%20forces%20in%20their%20project%20to%20devour%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20is%20signed%20by%20Vijoo%20Krishnan%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20and%20Ashok%20Dhawale%2C%20its%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710825567000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Faiks-rss-farmers-protests-freedom-struggle%22%2C%22summary%2