_6494655.jpg%3F20240319034738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmore-than-a-dozen-workers-trapped-in-one-of-russias-largest-gold-mines-13097847%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirteen%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20after%20a%20rock%20fall%20in%20a%20gold%20mine%20in%20Russia's%20Amur%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmore-than-a-dozen-workers-trapped-in-one-of-russias-largest-gold-mines-13097847%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmore-than-a-dozen-workers-trapped-in-one-of-russias-largest-gold-mines-13097847%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmore-than-a-dozen-workers-trapped-in-one-of-russias-largest-gold-mines-13097847%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20Batting%20for%20%E2%80%98Donor%20Privacy%E2%80%99%20Should%20Ring%20Alarm%20Bells%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16200455%2F24ffc5eb-3f57-4e78-babc-397f22336a8f.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20fully%20internalised%20the%20key%20message%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20electoral%20bonds.%20Addressing%20the%20media%20after%20announcing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20schedule%2C%20the%20CEC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-political-funding-arun-goels-resignation-cec-says-privacy-important%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20always%20in%20favour%20of%20transparency%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20democracy%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20no%20scope%20for%20hiding%20anything%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20any%20institutional%20mechanism%20for%20transparent%20election%20funding%20should%20also%20consider%20%E2%80%9Cprotecting%20donor%20privacy%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20not%20harassed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20articulating%20his%20position%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20CEC%20pretty%20much%20harked%20back%20to%20the%20utter%20illogic%20of%20then%20finance%20minister%20Arun%20Jaitley%E2%80%99s%20proposition%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20first%20mooted%20the%20new%20mechanism%20for%20election%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20contention%20has%20been%20demolished%20by%20former%20CEC%20S.Y.%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20asserts%20that%20corporates%20were%20funding%20political%20parties%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20with%20their%20names%20made%20public%20and%20no%20one%20ever%20complained%20of%20harassment.%20So%20this%20is%20an%20utterly%20specious%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20in%20a%20democracy%20transparency%20cannot%20be%20ensured%20by%20protecting%20the%20privacy%20of%20a%20political%20donor.%20They%20are%20fundamentally%20antithetical%20to%20each%20other.%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20was%20emphatic%20that%20the%20names%20of%20corporate%20donors%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20they%20donated%20to%20must%20be%20made%20public%20so%20that%20voters%20can%20make%20informed%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20seems%20to%20disagree%20with%20this%20aspect%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20and%20continues%20to%20hold%20that%20privacy%20must%20be%20afforded%20to%20big%20corporate%20donors.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20government%20line%20so%20far.%20Home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20so%20far%20admitted%20there%20may%20be%20weaknesses%20in%20the%20scheme%20and%20suggests%20improvement%20to%20make%20it%20more%20foolproof.%20The%20government%20also%20obliquely%20maintains%20the%20need%20for%20privacy%20protection%20while%20not%20openly%20disagreeing%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20motivation%20is%20for%20articulating%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20position%20is%20not%20very%20clear.%20Especially%20when%20there%20is%20mounting%20evidence%20that%20transparency%20in%20politics%20and%20governance%20cannot%20be%20maintained%20if%20donor%20privacy%20is%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20a%20Court-Monitored%20Probe%20on%20Quid%20Pro%20Quo%20Involving%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Is%20Needed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-a-court-monitored-probe-on-quid-pro-quo-involving-electoral-bonds-is-needed%5C%22%3EWhy%20a%20Court-Monitored%20Probe%20on%20Quid%20Pro%20Quo%20Involving%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Is%20Needed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20privacy%20argument%20is%20flawed%20on%20so%20many%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20spite%20of%20privacy%20being%20afforded%2C%20many%20top%20corporate%20groups%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Modi%20regime%20have%20not%20appeared%20as%20direct%20donors.%20Some%20have%20used%20unknown%20subsidiaries%20held%20privately%20by%20top%20employees%20as%20vehicles%20to%20make%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20the%20outcome%20of%20giving%20privacy%20to%20donors%3F%20Barring%20a%20few%20exceptions%2C%20many%20are%20still%20using%20front%20companies%20to%20donate%20political%20funds.%20This%20itself%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20argument%20in%20favour%20of%20donor%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20stock%20market-listed%20companies%20are%20subject%20to%20multiple%20governance%20rules%20under%20company%20law%20and%20the%20SEBI%20Act.%20A%20listed%20company%20cannot%20donate%20unlimited%20amounts%20to%20political%20parties%20as%20it%20is%20answerable%20to%20shareholders.%20For%20this%20reason%20alone%20there%20was%20a%20ceiling%20of%207.5%25%20of%20the%20previous%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20net%20profits%20for%20corporate%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20before%20electoral%20bonds%20came%20into%20being.%20The%20new%20arrangement%20did%20away%20with%20the%207.5%25%20ceiling%20precisely%20because%20the%20Modi%20government%20wanted%20to%20encourage%20big%20corporations%20to%20donate%20money%20through%20their%20private%2C%20unlisted%20front%20companies.%20Is%20this%20promoting%20transparency%3F%20Far%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20company%20law%20framework%20itself%20suffers%20from%20this%20weakness.%20Corporate%20groups%20can%20hide%20their%20multiple%20activities%20in%20many%20layered%20privately%20owned%20subsidiaries.%20A%20maze%20of%20hundreds%20of%20private%20family-owned%20companies%20hold%20shares%20of%20a%20bigger%20publicly%20listed%20entity.%20We%20all%20know%20about%20hundreds%20of%20unlisted%20subsidiaries%20having%20the%20same%20address%20as%20the%20main%20listed%20company.%20Information%20about%20these%20subsidiaries%20never%20appears%20in%20the%20main%20audited%20balance%20sheet%20of%20the%20group.%20This%20non-transparent%20arrangement%2C%20in%20some%20sense%2C%20has%20been%20quietly%20imported%20into%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%20No%20wonder%20in%20the%20list%20of%20donors%20made%20public%20so%20far%20there%20is%20a%20company%20reportedly%20owned%20by%20the%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20of%20Reliance%20Retail.%20An%20employee%20owning%20a%20subsidiary%20company%20is%20by%20itself%20a%20bit%20odd.%20This%20company%20donated%2010%20times%20its%20net%20profit.%20There%20could%20be%20many%20such%20examples%20as%20the%20full%20list%20is%20scrutinised.%20There%20is%20a%20stockbroker%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20contributed%20very%20large%20amounts%20as%20donations.%20By%20definition%2C%20brokers%20hold%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20money.%20No%20rocket%20science%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20transparency%20and%20privacy%20can%20never%20go%20together%20in%20corporate%20funding%20of%20political%20parties.%20The%20CEC%20would%20do%20well%20to%20absorb%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment.%20It%20will%20only%20enhance%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20institution%20he%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710819489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16200455%2F24ffc5eb-3f57-4e78-babc-397f22336a8f.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-batting-for-donor-privacy-should-ring-alarm-bells%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20articulating%20his%20position%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20CEC%20pretty%20much%20harked%20back%20to%20the%20utter%20illogic%20of%20then%20finance%20minister%20Arun%20Jaitley%E2%80%99s%20proposition%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20first%20mooted%20the%20new%20mechanism%20for%20election%20funding.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-batting-for-donor-privacy-should-ring-alarm-bells%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Har%20Mobile%20Pe%20Modi%3A%20PM's%20WhatsApp%20Message%20Raises%20Questions%20of%20Digital%20Influence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19084647%2Fwhatsapp-1357489_1920.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Modi%20is%20everywhere%20this%20election%20season%3B%20he%20is%20campaigning%20offline%2C%20online%20and%20would%20reach%20the%20quantum%20realm%20in%20a%20jiffy%20if%20it%20helps%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20win%20those%20400-plus%20MP%20seats%20for%20the%20upcoming%20parliament%20elections.%20The%20WhatsApp%20messages%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20sending%20us%20a%20letter%20to%20reply%20to%20him%20with%20feedback%20for%20the%20future%20is%20a%20great%20campaign%20strategy.%20Except%20it%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20with%20state%20resources%20for%20electioneering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WhatsApp%20messages%20that%20everyone%20received%20from%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%E2%80%9D%20seeking%20feedback%20of%2010%20years%20of%20Modi%20government%20were%20marked%20%E2%80%98public%20and%20government%20service%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20registered%20office%20address%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%20This%20campaign%20could%20ideally%20have%20emerged%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mygov.in%2Foverview%2F%5C%22%3EMyGov%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20citizen%20platform%20that%20was%20designed%20to%20bring%20participatory%20governance%20inside%20government.%20MyGov%20is%20part%20of%20Digital%20India%20Corporation%2C%20a%20Section%208%20company%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20431px)%2085vw%2C%20431px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19082258%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22431%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19082258%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM.png%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19082258%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM-159x300.png%20159w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19082258%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM-544x1024.png%20544w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screenshot%20with%20details%20of%20service%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20campaign%20messages%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20probably%20every%20Indian%20who%20has%20a%20WhatsApp%20account.%20But%20these%20WhatsApp%20messages%20are%20not%20the%20first%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20messaging%20campaigns%20being%20carried%20out%20using%20government%20resources%20at%20MyGov.%20The%20recent%20campaign%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpledge.mygov.in%2Fmera-pehla-vote%2F%5C%22%3EMera%20Pehla%20Vote%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20Desh%20Ke%20Liye%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20also%20being%20spearheaded%20by%20MyGov%20%E2%80%93%20a%20campaign%20announced%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20taking%20over%20the%20duties%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20citizens%20and%20voters%20based%20in%20India%2C%20these%20messages%20seem%20to%20have%20gone%20abroad%2C%20ideally%20sent%20to%20seek%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Funitedstatesofindia%2Fcomments%2F1bh3f94%2Fbjp_really_be_spending_tax_money_on_this%2F%5C%22%3Efeedback%20from%20Indian%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20not%20in%20India.%20Interestingly%20these%20messages%20have%20been%20forwarded%20to%20foreigners%20who%20are%20not%20voters%20in%20India%2C%20several%20of%20whom%20have%20been%20sharing%20their%20experiences%20of%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20327px)%2085vw%2C%20327px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22327%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22228%5C%22%3EThe%20residents%20of%20UAE%20who%20received%20these%20messages%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khaleejtimes.com%2Fuae%2Fuae-surprise-whatsapp-letter-from-indian-pm-modi-raises-questions-among-residents%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20shock%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20their%20information%20being%20used%20by%20a%20foreign%20government.%20The%20questions%20of%20privacy%20in%20India%20are%20being%20raised%20by%20foreign%20nationals%20who%20are%20clearly%20shocked%20receiving%20these%20messages.%20This%20action%20is%20largely%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20violation%2C%20with%20no%20one%20ready%20to%20question%20either%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20or%20the%20government%20of%20its%20practices.%20People%20are%20just%20wondering%20which%20databases%20are%20being%20used%20to%20harvest%20their%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20information%20of%20voters%20comes%20from%20multiple%20sources%3B%20it%20is%20an%20entire%20ecosystem%20consisting%20of%20the%20government%20machinery%2C%20data%20brokers%20and%20party%20workers%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20information%20often%20interchanges%20hands%2C%20with%20party%20data%20going%20to%20the%20government%20and%20government%20data%20going%20to%20brokers.%20What%20we%20are%20witnessing%20now%20is%20the%20usage%20of%20hybrid%20machinery%20for%20political%20campaigning%20with%20multiple%20sources%20of%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20under%20the%20new%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%202023%2C%20a%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20should%20have%20made%20rules%20to%20prepare%20for%20privacy-related%20violations%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%20Except%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20would%20report%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20which%20is%20the%20body%20violating%20these%20provisions%20to%20send%20WhatsApp%20messages%20to%20everyone.%20There%20is%20a%20merger%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20state%20machinery%20with%20no%20separation%20of%20party%20functions%20and%20state%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20mobile%20phones%20has%20been%20of%20strategic%20importance%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Digital%20India%20Mission.%20His%20policy%20of%20Jandhan%20Aadhaar%20Mobile%20(JAM)%20with%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20of%20welfare%20amount%2C%20with%20his%20promotion%20as%20the%20leader%20bringing%20them%20the%20money%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20success.%20The%20KYC%20push%20for%20both%20economic%20and%20security%20reasons%20has%20been%20strategically%20co-opted%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20promote%20their%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20noticed%20these%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20has%20written%20to%20Meta%2C%20with%20no%20information%20of%20them%20approaching%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20The%20Office%20of%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20refused%20to%20issue%20any%20comment%20about%20the%20WhatsApp%20messages%20from%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20been%20strategically%20avoiding%20questioning%20the%20role%20of%20data%20in%20elections%2C%20and%20has%20been%20silent%20on%20it%20since%20Cambridge%20Analytica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMeta%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20Indian%20Citizens%20with%20WhatsApp%20has%20been%20getting%20an%20automated%20message%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20verified%20Business%E2%80%9D%20named%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sampark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20talks%20about%20taking%20feedback%20from%20Citizens%2C%20but%20the%20attached%20PDF%20is%20nothing%20but%20political%20propaganda.%20(1%2F3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmzxYjYCsaD%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmzxYjYCsaD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Congress%20Kerala%20(%40INCKerala)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCKerala%2Fstatus%2F1768933455604371934%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatsApp%20and%20Facebook%20have%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20election-related%20issues%20in%20India%2C%20including%20the%20spread%20of%20hate%20speech%20and%20fake%20news.%20The%20BJP%20has%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20use%20the%20power%20of%20IT%20regulation%20to%20force%20these%20organisations%20to%20bend%20to%20their%20demands.%20The%20role%20of%20these%20digital%20platforms%20is%20reshaping%20our%20democracy%20is%20deeper%20than%20has%20been%20documented.%20WhatsApp%20with%20its%20policies%20on%20spam%2C%20misinformation%20and%20fake%20news%20continues%20to%20allow%20the%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20and%20is%20the%20favourite%20for%20every%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20goes%20beyond%20WhatsApp%20and%20privacy%2C%20with%20the%20usage%20of%20state%20funds%20for%20electioneering.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20election%20year%20is%20the%20role%20of%20influencers%20who%20can%20influence%20people%20through%20social%20media.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20become%20closer%20to%20many%20influencers.%20The%20National%20Creator%20Awards%2C%20also%20in%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finnovateindia.mygov.in%2Fnational-creators-award-2024%2F%5C%22%3EMyGov%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20been%20a%20programme%20to%20gain%20favour%20of%20these%20influencers%20to%20make%20them%20promote%20election%20related%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20regulation%20of%20micro-targeting%20and%20social%20media%20influence%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20a%20serious%20concern%20with%20no%20tangible%20solution%20in%20sight.%20The%20only%20body%20which%20is%20required%20to%20address%20these%20problems%20is%20in%20a%20slumber%20with%20no%20interest%20to%20address%20these%20emerging%20challenges.%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20also%20dis-interested%20in%20demanding%20regulation%2C%20with%20them%20attempting%20to%20copy%20the%20practices%20of%20BJP%20and%20failing%20badly%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20by%20ignoring%20to%20act%20on%20these%20issues%20is%20sending%20a%20message%3A%20it%20is%20okay%20for%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20do%20anything%20they%20want.%20The%20commission%20is%20effectively%20abdicating%20its%20responsibility%20of%20hosting%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20The%20upcoming%20elections%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20free%20or%20even%20fair%2C%20with%20unequal%20influence%20of%20social%20media%20and%20Indians%20at%20large%20using%20digital%20tools%20and%20state%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710818234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19084647%2Fwhatsapp-1357489_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fhar-mobile-pe-modi-pms-whatsapp-message-raises-questions-of-digital-influence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20issue%20goes%20beyond%20WhatsApp%20and%20privacy%2C%20with%20the%20usage%20of%20state%20funds%20for%20electioneering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fhar-mobile-pe-modi-pms-whatsapp-message-raises-questions-of-digital-influence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajay%20Devgn%E2%80%99s%20NY%20VFXWaala%20Acquires%20Stake%20in%20Sweden%E2%80%99s%20Goodbye%20Kansas%2C%20Launches%20Joint