lkswagen-chattanooga-union-election-uaw_n_65f760dae4b0defe9b27660d%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20Makes%20It%20Easy%20For%20People%20To%20Find%20The%20Right%20Lawyers%3B%20Earns%20Rs%201.25%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shreya%20Sharma%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20lawyer%20from%20Pune%2C%20met%20a%20woman%20in%20her%20fifties%20who%20was%20facing%20a%20property%20dispute%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20one%20to%20advise%20her.%20The%20woman%20was%20clueless%20about%20which%20lawyer%20to%20approach%2C%20what%20the%20procedure%20would%20entail%2C%20and%20this%20only%20added%20to%20her%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20Indians%20who%20face%20similar%20legal%20conundrums%2C%20as%20legal%20literacy%20remains%20poor.%20Recognising%20this%20gap%2C%20and%20to%20enable%20access%20to%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shreya%20started%20%E2%80%98Rest%20The%20Case%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20legal%20aggregator%20platform%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20found%20her%20calling%20when%20she%20was%20working%20on%20a%20project%20which%20involved%20interviewing%20lawyers%20as%20a%20student%20at%20Cardiff%20University.%20She%20searched%20for%20legal%20information%20online%2C%20and%20found%20many%20credible%20websites%20offering%20this%2C%20along%20with%20a%20list%20of%20lawyers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20was%20something%20like%20this%20available%20in%20India%3F%20The%2025-year-old%20found%20that%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20The%20Case%20provides%20legal%20information%2C%20from%20basic%20templates%20to%20bare%20acts%2C%20legal%20drafting%2C%20and%20a%20list%20of%20lawyers.%20It%20has%20also%20created%20a%20network%20base%20for%20lawyers%20of%20different%20specialisations%20to%20connect%20with%20clients.%20More%20than%201%2C200%20lawyers%20from%20across%20the%20country%20are%20already%20a%20part%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shreya%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20charge%20anything%20from%20clients%2C%20she%20has%20created%20different%20packages%20for%20lawyers%2C%20making%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.25%20crores%20in%20the%202022-23%20financial%20year%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20aim%2C%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20is%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20legal%20information%20with%20just%20a%20click.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESimplifying%20legal%20jargon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreya%20Sharma%20started%20Rest%20The%20Case%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreya%20Sharma%20started%20Rest%20The%20Case%20in%202021.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ease%20of%20access%20when%20it%20came%20to%20finding%20legal%20help%20in%20the%20UK%20is%20what%20stayed%20with%20Shreya%20the%20most.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20these%20websites%20very%20interesting%20as%20I%20had%20not%20seen%20something%20like%20this%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20looked%20for%20similar%20websites%20in%20India%2C%20or%20a%20single%20website%20which%20would%20provide%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315357%2Fmanilal-doctor-revolutionary-leader-freed-indentured-indian-labourers-in-fiji-mauritius%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20one.%20She%20then%20decided%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20by%20building%20the%20solution%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20initial%20funding%20from%20her%20father%2C%20Shreya%20hired%20a%20few%20interns%20and%20built%20the%20website%20for%20Rest%20The%20Case%20after%20returning%20to%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra.%20She%20ensured%20that%20every%20information%20posted%20on%20the%20website%20was%20written%20by%20a%20lawyer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20idea%20with%20Rest%20The%20Case%20is%20to%20provide%20vetted%20information%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20which%20the%20internet%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide.%20I%20have%20created%20one%20place%20where%20you%20can%20find%20everything%20from%20basic%20information%2C%20how%20to%20file%20a%20case%20to%20which%20lawyer%20to%20choose.%20We%20individually%20talk%20to%20clients%20before%20sharing%20their%20information%20with%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20was%20getting%20lawyers%20onboard.%20The%20then%2021-year-old%20would%20knock%20on%20their%20doors%20and%20explain%20her%20vision.%20Initially%2C%20many%20dismissed%20her%20or%20her%20id