%5C%22%3EWhy%20appropriate%20exposure%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreya%20Sharma%20wants%20to%20simplify%20legal%20jargon%20and%20make%20legal%20aid%20accessible%20to%20all%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-2-1710763616-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345067%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreya%20Sharma%20wants%20to%20simplify%20legal%20jargon%20and%20make%20legal%20aid%20accessible%20with%20a%20single%20click.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20a%20family%20of%2010%2C%20Shreya%20grew%20up%20around%20entrepreneurial%20mindsets%20and%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20where%20everybody%20works.%20My%20father%20runs%20educational%20institutions%20and%C2%A0%20everyone%20has%20a%20tremendous%20drive%2C%20working%20day%20in%2C%20day%20out.%20I%20have%20been