vaad%20organises%20a%20grand%20inaugural%20show%20every%20year%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20This%20year%2C%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhols%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20musical%20instruments%20reverberated%20in%20homage%20to%20Birsa%20Munda.%20The%20tribals%20adorning%20bright%20yellow%20vests%20with%20white%20%3Cem%3Edhotis%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20played%20various%20goosebump-inducing%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebonga%20taal%2C%20baika%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esantal%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDancers%20and%20singers%20participated%20in%20cultural%20performances%20as%20people%20gorged%20on%20tribal%20delicacies%2C%20shopped%20for%20vibrant%20artefacts%20(handcrafted%20by%20the%20same%20artisans%20who%20are%20selling%20them)%2C%20and%20danced%20to%20the%20tribal%20beats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Samvaad%20since%20the%20beginning.%20I%20love%20the%20energy%20here.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20highlight%20is%20selling%20our%20Oraon%20paintings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20a%20painter%20from%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20few%20people%20knew%20about%20our%20paintings%20before%2C%20but%20now%20it%20is%20more%20popular.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20only%20handicrafts%20stalls%2C%20but%20Samvaad%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20with%20%3Cem%3EAkhara%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fellowship%2C%20tribal%20healers%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Choisa%20Hakong%20from%20the%20Chakesang%20tribe%20(Nagaland)%20was%20at%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CSamvaad%20is%20connecting%20tribals%20as%20one%20in%20spirit%20and%20culture.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20attend%20and%20showcase%20our%20products%20made%20from%20teak%20and%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20five%20days%2C%20Pritesh%2C%20Sumanti%2C%20and%20Choisa%2C%20along%20with%20people%20from%20110%20other%20tribes%2C%20displayed%20their%20cuisine%2C%20artwork%2C%20and%20healing%20practices.%20Besides%20the%20stalls%2C%20140%20home%20chefs%20from%2037%20tribes%20offered%20home%20delivery%20via%20the%20Zomato%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20these%20artisans%20goes%20beyond%20selling%20their%20products.%20They%20also%20refine%20their%20skills%20through%20workshops%20and%20sessions%20led%20by%20handicraft%20experts%2C%20engage%20in%20healing%20practices%2C%20and%20showcase%20their%20culinary%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tribal%20food%20at%20display%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETribal%20food%20displayed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tangible%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20seen%20a%20visible%20impact%2C%20bringing%20together%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%20The%20beauty%20of%20this%20conclave%20is%20that%20it%20extends%20beyond%20the%20five%20days%3B%20the%20dialogue%20and%20actions%20continue%20throughout%20the%20year.%20This%20meticulous%20approach%20has%20led%20to%20outcomes%20that%20once%20seemed%20far-fetched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%E2%80%98Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ensemble%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121371%2Fanahad-tribal-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country%20composed%20and%20launched%20five%20original%20compositions%20on%20a%20tribal%20narrative%20at%20the%20conclave.%20The%20compositions%20are%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20unifying%20tribals%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%20They%20include%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENukhtharini%20Juwmang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Rabha%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEklaivet%20Ajakong%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Karbi%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDela%20Dela%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Santal%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbua%20Disom%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Ho%20tribe%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20outcome%20of%20Samvaad%E2%80%99s%20ten-year%20journey%20was%20seen%20in%20Jaincy%20John%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20conventional%20narrative%20of%20urban%20education.%20Living%20in%20cities%20often%20limits%20our%20view%20of%20education%20to%20securing